View McTefOperations
Query
 
CREATE VIEW [dbo].[${schemaName}.${viewName}]
AS
SELECT     
	TefOperations.ID,
	Users.Code AS UserCode,
	Users.Name AS UserName,
	Titles.Code AS CustomerCode,
	(
		CASE
			WHEN Vouchers.Visitor IS NOT NULL THEN Vouchers.Visitor
			ELSE Members.[Name]
		END
	) AS CustomerName,
	(
		CASE
			WHEN Vouchers.Voucher IS NOT NULL THEN Vouchers.Voucher
			ELSE Duns.NN
		END
	) AS Info,
	(
		CASE
			WHEN Vouchers.Voucher IS NOT NULL THEN 'Voucher'
			ELSE 'NN'
		END
	) AS InfoLabel,
	OperationsAnalysis.AntiFraudType,
	OperationsAnalysis.AntiFraudStatus,
	OperationsAnalysis.AuthenticationAcquirerType,
	OperationsAnalysis.AuthenticationStatus
FROM
	[MultiClubes].dbo.TefOperations
	LEFT JOIN [MultiClubes].Tef.OperationsAnalysis ON TefOperations.Id=OperationsAnalysis.Operation
	LEFT JOIN
	(
		[MultiClubes].dbo.Titles
		JOIN [MultiClubes].dbo.Members ON Titles.ID=Members.Title AND Members.Titular=1
	) ON TefOperations.Title=Titles.ID
	JOIN [MultiClubes].dbo.Users ON TefOperations.UserId=Users.ID
	OUTER APPLY
	(
		SELECT TOP(1)
			Duns.NN
		FROM
			[MultiClubes].dbo.PaymentItems
			JOIN [MultiClubes].dbo.DunPayments ON PaymentItems.Payment=DunPayments.Payment
			JOIN [MultiClubes].dbo.Duns ON DunPayments.Dun=Duns.ID
		WHERE
			PaymentItems.TefOperation=TefOperations.ID
	) AS Duns
	OUTER APPLY
	(
		SELECT TOP(1)
			Vouchers.Code AS Voucher,
			Vouchers.VisitDate AS DataVisita,
			Visitors.[Name] AS Visitor
		FROM 
			[MultiClubes].dbo.Vouchers
			JOIN [MultiClubes].dbo.Visitors ON Vouchers.Visitor=Visitors.ID
			JOIN [MultiClubes].dbo.VoucherSales ON Vouchers.ID=VoucherSales.Voucher
			JOIN [MultiClubes].dbo.Parcels ON VoucherSales.Sale=Parcels.Sale
			JOIN [MultiClubes].dbo.ParcelPayments ON ParcelPayments.Parcel=Parcels.ID
			JOIN [MultiClubes].dbo.Payments ON ParcelPayments.Payment=Payments.ID
			JOIN [MultiClubes].dbo.PaymentItems ON Payments.ID=PaymentItems.Payment
		WHERE
			PaymentItems.TefOperation=TefOperations.ID
	) AS Vouchers
IdxColumn NameData Type
  ID int
  UserCode nvarchar
  UserName nvarchar
  CustomerCode nvarchar
  CustomerName nvarchar
  Info nvarchar
  InfoLabel varchar
  AntiFraudType tinyint
  AntiFraudStatus tinyint
  AuthenticationAcquirerType tinyint
  AuthenticationStatus tinyint

View PromoterConsumptions
Query
 
-- View utilizada nos relatrios de receita por promotor e por gerente
-- Retorna os consumos relacionados ao promotor

CREATE VIEW [dbo].[PromoterConsumptions]
AS
SELECT
	Invoices.SourceNumber AS Promoter,
	AccountMovements.[DateTime],
	Product.Name AS Product,
	SaleItems.Quantity,
	SaleItems.SubTotal,
	(
		CASE 
			WHEN Product.ProductType IN (4,6,7) THEN CAST(1 AS BIT)
			ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
		END
	) AS IsService
FROM
	DayUserCards
	JOIN AccountMovements 
	ON 
	(
		DayUserCards.AccountNumber=AccountMovements.AccountNumber 
		AND DayUserCards.LegacyOrigin = 'MULTICLUBES'
	)
	JOIN Invoices ON 
	(
		AccountMovements.InvoiceNumber=Invoices.InvoiceNumber 
		AND AccountMovements.MovementType=0
		AND AccountMovements.Origin=0
	)
	JOIN Sales
	ON
	(
		AccountMovements.OperationUid=Sales.SaleUid 
		AND Sales.CanceledManager IS NULL
	)
	JOIN SaleItems 
	ON
	(
		Sales.SaleNumber=SaleItems.SaleNumber
		AND SaleItems.CancelManager IS NULL
	)
	JOIN Products Product ON SaleItems.Product=Product.Id 
WHERE
	Invoices.SourceType=1
	AND AccountMovements.IsReversed = 0
	
UNION

SELECT
	Invoices.SourceNumber AS Promoter,
	AccountMovements.[DateTime],
	IncreaseCharges.Name AS Product,
	NULL AS Quantity,
	SaleItemIncreaseCharges.Value AS SubTotal,
	CAST(1 AS BIT) as IsService
FROM
	DayUserCards 
	JOIN AccountMovements 
	ON 
	(
		DayUserCards.AccountNumber=AccountMovements.AccountNumber 
		AND DayUserCards.LegacyOrigin='MULTICLUBES'
	)
	JOIN Invoices
	ON 
	(
		AccountMovements.InvoiceNumber=Invoices.InvoiceNumber 
		AND AccountMovements.MovementType=0 
		AND AccountMovements.Origin=0
	) 
	JOIN Sales
	ON
	(
		AccountMovements.OperationUid=Sales.SaleUid 
		AND Sales.CanceledManager IS NULL
	)
	JOIN SaleItems ON Sales.SaleNumber=SaleItems.SaleNumber
	JOIN SaleItemIncreaseCharges 
	ON
	(
		SaleItems.SaleNumber=SaleItemIncreaseCharges.SaleNumber
		AND SaleItems.ItemNumber=SaleItemIncreaseCharges.ItemNumber
	)
	JOIN IncreaseCharges ON SaleItemIncreaseCharges.IncreaseCharge=IncreaseCharges.Id
WHERE
	Invoices.SourceType=1
	AND AccountMovements.IsReversed = 0
IdxColumn NameData Type
  Promoter int
  DateTime datetime
  Product nvarchar
  Quantity decimal
  SubTotal decimal
  IsService bit


View TMP_EVENT_TRANSFERS_LOG
Query
 
-- Cria a view detalhando o log de operaes de transferncias realizadas
-- Uso: 
-- SELECT * FROM TMP_EVENT_TRANSFERS_LOG

CREATE VIEW TMP_EVENT_TRANSFERS_LOG AS
SELECT
	Hotels.[Name] AS Hotel,
	ReserveAccountInfo.HotelRoomNumber AS Quarto,
	Guest.AccountNumber,
	Guest.Code AS Cartao,
	Guest.CustomerName AS Hospede,
	Cancellations.DateTime AS DataCancelamento,
	CancelUser.Name AS UsuarioCancelamento,
	Sales.ClosingDateTime AS DataVenda,
	SaleUser.Name AS UsuarioVenda,
	Products.MainBarcode AS CodProduto,
	Products.Name AS Produto,
	SaleItems.Quantity AS Quantidade,
	(
		CASE
			WHEN SaleItems.ChangedUnitPriceManager IS NULL THEN SaleItems.UnitPrice
			ELSE SaleItems.ChangedUnitPrice
		END
	) AS PrecoUnitario,
	COALESCE(SaleItems.RatedDiscount,0) + COALESCE(SaleItemIncreaseCharges.RatedDiscount,0) AS Desconto,
	COALESCE(SaleItemIncreaseCharges.Value,0) AS Acrescimos,
	
	(
		(
			SaleItems.Quantity *
			(
				CASE
					WHEN SaleItems.ChangedUnitPriceManager IS NULL THEN SaleItems.UnitPrice
					ELSE SaleItems.ChangedUnitPrice
				END
			)
		)
		- (COALESCE(SaleItems.RatedDiscount,0) + COALESCE(SaleItemIncreaseCharges.RatedDiscount,0)) 
		+ (COALESCE(SaleItemIncreaseCharges.Value,0))
	) AS Total

FROM 
	Cancellations
	JOIN AccountMovements AS TransferOriginMovement ON Cancellations.TransferOriginMovementNumber=TransferOriginMovement.MovementNumber
	JOIN AccountMovements AS TransferDestinMovement ON Cancellations.TransferDestinMovementNumber=TransferDestinMovement.MovementNumber
	JOIN Users AS CancelUser ON Cancellations.CancelManager=CancelUser.Id
	JOIN SaleItems ON Cancellations.Id=SaleItems.Cancellation
	JOIN Sales ON SaleItems.SaleNumber=Sales.SaleNumber
	JOIN Users AS SaleUser ON Sales.[User]=SaleUser.Id
	JOIN Products ON SaleItems.Product=Products.Id

	OUTER APPLY
	(
		SELECT 
			SUM(Value) AS Value,
			SUM(COALESCE(RatedDiscount, 0)) AS RatedDiscount
		FROM
			SaleItemIncreaseCharges
		WHERE
			SaleItemIncreaseCharges.SaleNumber=SaleItems.SaleNumber
			AND SaleItemIncreaseCharges.ItemNumber=SaleItems.ItemNumber
	) AS SaleItemIncreaseCharges

	JOIN DayUserCards AS Guest ON TransferOriginMovement.AccountNumber=Guest.AccountNumber
	JOIN Accounts AS GuestAccount ON Guest.AccountNumber=GuestAccount.AccountNumber

	LEFT JOIN
	(
		AccountsInfo AS ReserveAccountInfo
		LEFT JOIN HotelShops ON ReserveAccountInfo.HotelEid=HotelShops.HotelEid
		LEFT JOIN Shops AS Hotels ON Hotels.Id=HotelShops.Shop
	) ON GuestAccount.AccountInfo=ReserveAccountInfo.Id
IdxColumn NameData Type
  Hotel nvarchar
  Quarto nvarchar
  AccountNumber int
  Cartao bigint
  Hospede nvarchar
  DataCancelamento datetime
  UsuarioCancelamento nvarchar
  DataVenda datetime
  UsuarioVenda nvarchar
  CodProduto nvarchar
  Produto nvarchar
  Quantidade decimal
  PrecoUnitario decimal
  Desconto decimal
  Acrescimos decimal
  Total decimal


View V_LOGVENDASTEF
Query
 
-- dbo.V_LOGVENDASTEF source

--Exportao
CREATE VIEW dbo.V_LOGVENDASTEF AS
select 
	'MULTICLUBES' as sistemaOrigem,
	convert(varchar,(right(replicate('0',7) + convert(varchar, (row_number() over (order by id))),7))) as sequencia,
	CONVERT(CHAR(8),tt.DateTime, 112) data,
	convert(varchar,replace(CONVERT(CHAR(8),tt.DateTime, 108),':','')) as hora,
	convert(varchar,right(replicate('0',15) + replace(convert(varchar,(tt.Value)),'.',''),15)) valorTransacao,
	convert(varchar,'000000000000000') valorComplementar,
	convert(varchar,right(replicate('0',19) + convert(varchar,isnull(tt.cardNumber,0)),19)) as numeroCartao,
	convert(varchar,right(replicate('0',13) + convert(varchar,tt.nsu),13)) nsutef,
	convert(varchar,right(replicate('0',12) + convert(varchar,isnull(tt.sitefnsu,0)),12)) as nsuOperadora,
	convert(varchar,'0000000000000') pdvted,
	replicate('0', 13-len(isnull(substring(cast(cast(tt.ShopCode as numeric) as char),1,10),'0'))) + isnull(substring(cast(cast(tt.ShopCode as numeric) as char),1,10),'0') pdvOperadora,
	convert(varchar,right(replicate('0',2) + convert(varchar,isnull(tt.ParcelQty,0)),2)) qtdParcelas,
	convert(varchar,right(replicate('0',6) + convert(varchar,isnull(tt.AuthNumber,0)),6)) codAutorizacao,
	convert(varchar,'00') codResposta,
	convert(varchar,
	case 
/*		when tt.CardType='AMEX' then '030'
		when tt.AuthInstitution='CIELO' and tt.CardType<>'AMEX' then '060'
		when tt.AuthInstitution='GETNET' and tt.CardType<>'AMEX' then '100'
		when tt.AuthInstitution='REDE' and tt.CardType<>'AMEX' then '010'
		when tt.AuthInstitution='REDECARD' and tt.CardType<>'AMEX' then '010'
		else  '060'*/
		when tt.AuthInstitution='CIELO'     then '060' --and tt.CardType<>'AMEX' then '060'
		when tt.AuthInstitution='GETNET'    then '100' --and tt.CardType<>'AMEX'
		when tt.AuthInstitution='REDE'      then '010' --and tt.CardType<>'AMEX'
		when tt.AuthInstitution='REDECARD'  then '010' --and tt.CardType<>'AMEX'
		else  '060'		
	end) as codOperadora,
	convert(varchar,'01540533000129') as cnpj,
	convert(varchar,' ' ) as filer,
	convert(varchar,
	case
		when tt.PaymentType like '%CRDITO%' and isnull(tt.ParcelQty,1) =1 and tt.isCancel=0 then '1'
		when tt.PaymentType like '%CRDITO%' and isnull(tt.ParcelQty,1) >1 and tt.isCancel=0 then '3'
		when tt.PaymentType like '%DBITO%' and tt.isCancel=0 then '2'
		when tt.isCancel=1 then '4'
		else '2'
	end) as codTransacao,
	convert(varchar,
	case
		when tt.CardType='AMEX' then '05'
		when tt.CardType='BANESCARD' then '21'
		when tt.CardType='BANRICOMPRAS' then '04'
		when tt.CardType='CABAL DEBITO' OR tt.CardType='CABALCRED' then '06'
		when tt.CardType='CARTAO CREDITO' OR tt.CardType='CARTAO DEBITO' or tt.CardType='DESCONHECIDO' then '99'
		when tt.CardType='CREDZ' then '24'
		when tt.CardType='DINERS' then '09'
		when tt.CardType='DISCOVER' then '10'
		when tt.CardType='ELO' OR tt.CardType='ELO CREDITO' or tt.CardType='ELO DEBITO' then '07'
		when tt.CardType='HIPERCARD' then '03'
		when tt.CardType='MAESTRO' OR tt.CardType='MASTERCARD'  then '02'
		when tt.CardType='MAIS' then '13'
		when tt.CardType='REFEICAO' then '30'
		when tt.CardType='SOROCREDCR' then '08'
		when tt.CardType='VISA' OR tt.CardType='VISA CREDITO' or tt.CardType='VISA ELECTRON' then '01'
		else '99'
	end) as bandeira,
	convert(varchar,case
		when exists(select 1 from MultiVendas.dbo.TefTransactions tt2 where tt.id=tt2.CanceledTefTransaction) then '3'
		else '1'
	end) as situacaoTransacao,
	convert(varchar,'0000000') as notaFiscal,
	convert(varchar,right(replicate('0',20) + convert(varchar,isnull(tt."Transaction",0)),20)) tid,
	convert(varchar,'00000000000000000000') as bpagid,
	convert(varchar,case
		when tt.CardType='AMEX' and (tt.ParcelType=null or tt.ParcelType=' VISTA') then '029'
		when tt.CardType='AMEX' and tt.ParcelType='PARCELADO ESTABELECIMENTO' then '030'
		when tt.CardType='BANESCARD' and (tt.ParcelType=null or tt.ParcelType=' VISTA') then '003'
		when tt.CardType='BANESCARD' and (tt.ParcelType is not null or tt.ParcelType<>' VISTA') then '004'
		when tt.CardType='BANRICOMPRAS' and (tt.ParcelType=null or tt.ParcelType=' VISTA') then '100'
		when tt.CardType='BANRICOMPRAS' and (tt.ParcelType is not null or tt.ParcelType<>' VISTA') then '101'
		when tt.CardType='CABAL DEBITO' and tt.ParcelType=' VISTA' then '096'
		when tt.CardType='CABALCRED' and tt.ParcelType=' VISTA' then '097'
		when tt.CardType='CABALCRED' and tt.ParcelType='PARCELADO ESTABELECIMENTO' then '098'
		when tt.CardType='CARTAO CREDITO' or tt.CardType='CARTAO DEBITO' or tt.CardType='DESCONHECIDO' or tt.CardType='MAIS' then '000'
		when tt.CardType='CREDZ' and tt.ParcelType=' VISTA' then '006'
		when (tt.CardType='DINERS' or tt.CardType='Diners') and (tt.ParcelType=null or tt.ParcelType=' VISTA' or tt.ParcelType='Diners crdito  vista') then '020'
		when (tt.CardType='DINERS' or tt.CardType='Diners') and (tt.ParcelType='Diners parcelado loja' or tt.ParcelType='PARCELADO ESTABELECIMENTO') then '021'
		when tt.CardType='DISCOVER' and tt.ParcelType=' VISTA' then '019'
		when tt.CardType='ELO DEBITO' then '071'
		when tt.CardType='ELO CREDITO' and (tt.ParcelType=null or tt.ParcelType=' VISTA') then '070'
		when tt.CardType='ELO CREDITO' and tt.ParcelType='PARCELADO ESTABELECIMENTO' then '072'
		when tt.CardType='HIPERCARD' then '093'
		when tt.CardType='JCB' then '033'
		when tt.CardType='MAESTRO' or (tt.CardType='Mastercard' and tt.ParcelType='Maestro') then '011'
		when (tt.CardType='MASTERCARD' and (tt.ParcelType=null or tt.ParcelType=' VISTA')) or (tt.CardType='Mastercard' and tt.ParcelType='MasterCard crdito  vista') then '010'
		when (tt.CardType='MASTERCARD' and tt.ParcelType='PARCELADO ESTABELECIMENTO') or (tt.CardType='Mastercard' and tt.ParcelType='MasterCard parcelado loja') then '012'
		when (tt.CardType='REFEICAO') then '986'
		when tt.CardType='SOROCREDCR' and (tt.ParcelType=null or tt.ParcelType=' VISTA') then '061'
		when tt.CardType='SOROCREDCR' and (tt.ParcelType=null or tt.ParcelType='PARCELADO ESTABELECIMENTO') then '062'
		when tt.CardType='VISA ELECTRON' or (tt.CardType='VISA' and tt.ParcelType='Visa Electron Dbito  Vista') then '041'
		when (tt.CardType='VISA' or tt.CardType='VISA CREDITO') and (tt.ParcelType=null or tt.ParcelType=' VISTA' or tt.ParcelType='Visa Crdito  Vista') then '040'
		when (tt.CardType='VISA' or tt.CardType='VISA CREDITO') and (tt.ParcelType=null or tt.ParcelType='PARCELADO ESTABELECIMENTO' or tt.ParcelType='Visa Parcelado Loja') then '043'
		else '000'
	end) as produto,
	convert(varchar,case
		when tt.Type=2 then '1'
		when  tt.Type=1  then '5'
		when tt.SourceType<>4 and (tt.CardType='CARTAO CREDITO' or tt.CardType='CARTAO DEBITO') then '2'
		else '3'
	end) as tipoCaptura,
	'03'+right(replicate('0',33) + cast(isnull(tt.id,0) as varchar),33) as identificadorUnico,-- consultar arquivo identificadorSistemaUnico.xlsx
	convert(varchar,'000000000000000') as nsuOperadorStone,
	convert(varchar,'      ') as filer2
from 
	MultiVendas.dbo.TefTransactions tt
where
	cast(tt.DateTime as date)= dateadd(day,-1,cast(getdate () as date)) and
	tt.canceledTefTransaction is null and
	not exists(select 1 from MultiVendas.dbo.TefTransactions tc where tt.id=tc.CanceledTefTransaction and cast(tt.DateTime as date)=CAST(tc.DateTime AS DATE))

View v_consultapreco
Query
 
CREATE view ${schemaName}.${viewName} as 
select pp.FinalPrice as preco,count(*) as qtd,convert(varchar,p.name) as descricao,convert(varchar,bc.Code) as codigoBarra
from 
	products p

	join ProductPrices pp on p.id=pp.Product
group by p.name,bc.Code,pp.FinalPrice

(SELECT distinct
		e.Cnpj,

		si.ItemNumber,
		cs.OpeningDateTime as DataMovimento,
		s.ClosingDateTime as DataHoraVenda,
		sh.name as Loja,
		us.Name as Operador,
		c2.Name as Categoria,
		c1.name as Subcategoria1,
		c.name as Subcategoria2,
		case cast(p.ProductType as char(1))
			when '0' then 'Produto'
			when '4' then 'Servio'
			when '5' then 'Produto'
			when '6' then 'Servio'
			when '7' then 'Servio'
			else cast(p.ProductType as char(1))
		end as TipoProduto,
		isnull(p.LegacyCode,p.MainBarcode) as CodigoProduto,
		p.Name as descricaoProduto,
		t.Percentage as Aliquota,
		p.Ncm,
		p.Cest,
		p.Cfop,
		si.Quantity*COALESCE(tf.TransferMovementType,1) as quantidade,
		si.UnitPrice*COALESCE(tf.TransferMovementType,1) as valorUnitario,
		si.SubTotal*COALESCE(tf.TransferMovementType,1) as subtotal,
		isnull(sii.Value,0)*COALESCE(tf.TransferMovementType,1) as Acrescimo,
		(si.SubTotal+isnull(sii.Value,0)) *COALESCE(tf.TransferMovementType,1) as valorTotal,
		si.RatedDiscount  *COALESCE(tf.TransferMovementType,1) as desconto,

			when si.reversalOperationNumber is null then 'N'
			else 'S'

			when s.Cancellation is not null or s.CanceledManager is not null then 'S'

		join products p on si.Product=p.id

		join shops sh on cs.Shop=sh.Id
		join shops e on sh.Root=e.Id
		join users us on s.[User]=us.Id
		left Join Categories c1 on c.parent=c1.id
		left join categories c2 on c1.parent=c2.id
		left join Taxations t on p.Taxation=t.id
		left join AccountMovements am on s.SaleUid=am.OperationUid
		left join 
		(select 
				am.MovementNumber,
				am.TransferMovementType,
				am.AccountNumber as ContaOrigem,
				amt2.AccountNumber as ContaDestino
			FROM	
				AccountMovements am
				left join AccountMovements amt2 on am.TransferMovementNumber=amt2.MovementNumber and am.MovementType=amt2.MovementType and amt2.TransferMovementType=1
		) tf on am.MovementNumber=tf.MovementNumber
		--left --Apenas vendas para cartes Day Users
		left join 
			(select du.accountnumber,du.code
				from DayUserCards du
			union all
			select du.accountnumber,du.code
				from customers du) cO on tf.ContaOrigem=co.AccountNumber
		left join 
			(select du.accountnumber,du.code
				from DayUserCards du
			union all
			select du.accountnumber,du.code
				from customers du) cd on tf.contaDestino=cd.AccountNumber
		left join SaleItemIncreaseCharges sii on si.SaleNumber=sii.SaleNumber and si.ItemNumber=sii.ItemNumber
		left join Cancellations cas on isnull(si.Cancellation,s.Cancellation)=cas.Id
		left join users usc on isnull(cas.CancelManager,isnull(si.CancelManager,s.CanceledManager))=usc.id
	WHERE
		--cast(s.ClosingDateTime as date)=cast(getdate()-2 as date) and
		--sh.Name='Marolo Caf' and
		 PreSaleNumber is not null

		'MULTIVENDAS' as sistemaOrigem,
		s.SaleNumber as SaleNumber,
		si.ItemNumber,
		cs.OpeningDateTime as DataMovimento,
		s.ClosingDateTime as DataHoraVenda,
		sh.name as Loja,
		us.Name as Operador,
		c2.Name as Categoria,
		c1.name as Subcategoria1,
		c.name as Subcategoria2,
		case cast(p.ProductType as char(1))
			when '0' then 'Produto'
			when '4' then 'Servio'
			when '5' then 'Produto'
			when '6' then 'Servio'
			when '7' then 'Servio'
			else cast(p.ProductType as char(1))
		end as TipoProduto,

			else 'S'

		join shops sh on cs.Shop=sh.Id

				AccountMovements am
				left join AccountMovements amt1 on am.MovementNumber=amt1.RelatedMovementNumber and amt1.TransferMovementType=-1
				left join AccountMovements amt2 on amt1.TransferMovementNumber=amt2.MovementNumber
			where am.MovementType=0) am on s.SaleUid=am.OperationUid
		--left --Apenas vendas para cartes Day Users
		left join SaleItemIncreaseCharges sii on si.SaleNumber=sii.SaleNumber and si.ItemNumber=sii.ItemNumber
		left join Cancellations cas on isnull(si.Cancellation,s.Cancellation)=cas.Id
		left join users usc on isnull(cas.CancelManager,isnull(si.CancelManager,s.CanceledManager))=usc.id
	WHERE
		--cast(s.ClosingDateTime as date)=cast(getdate()-2 as date) and
		s.SaleType in(0,6)) a
where
	cast(DataHoraVenda as date)=cast(getdate()-1 as date)
--	cast(DataHoraVenda as date) between cast(getdate()-23 as date) and cast(getdate()-7 as date)	
--	cast(DataHoraVenda as date)=cast(getdate()-54 as date)

View v_fiscalEN
Query
 
CREATE view ${schemaName}.${viewName} as 
select distinct
	  nfs.id as idNF,
	  nfs.[DateTime] AS DATAHORA,
	  case 
	  	WHEN nfs.[Type]=3 then 'NFS-e'
	  	when nfs.[Type]=2 then 'NFC-e'
	  end as tipoNota,
	  nfs.Serie,
	  nfs.NfNumber as numeroNota,
	  nfs.[Key] as chave,
	  nfs.Total as valor,
	  case Status
	  	when 0 then 'Pendente Envio'
	  	when 1 then 'No identificado'
	  	when 2 then 'Rejeitado em Contingncia'
	  	when 3 then 'Autorizado em Contingncia'
	  	when 4 then 'No identificado'
	  	when 6 then 'Expirado'
	  	when 7 then 'Inutilizado'
	  	when 8 then 'Autorizado'
	  	when 9 then 'RPS'
	  else 
	  	'No identificado'
	  end as status,
	isnull(ps.AccountNumber,-1) as numConta,
	ps.CcfSaleNumber as saleNumber,
	isnull (e.Cnpj,sh.cnpj) as cnpj,
	'MULTIVENDAS' as sistemaOrigem
	from 
	nfs
	join shops sh on nfs.Shop=sh.Id
	left join shops e on sh.Root=e.Id
	left join PreSalesNfs psn on nfs.id=psn.Nf
	left join PreSales ps on ps.PreSaleNumber=psn.PreSaleNumber
where 
	cast(nfs.[DateTime] as date)>=cast(getdate()-1 as date)
--	cast(nfs.[DateTime] as date) between cast(getdate()-3 as date) and cast(getdate()-1 as date)
IdxColumn NameData Type

  chave nvarchar
  valor decimal
  status varchar

  saleNumber int

		when ai.HotelEid='HPOUSADA' then '01.540.533/0001-29'
		when ai.HotelEid='CRISTAL' then '01.540.533/0001-29'
		when ai.HotelEid='RQSFI' then '01.540.533/0001-29'
		when ai.HotelEid='RQSFIII' then '01.540.533/0001-29'
		when ai.HotelEid='GIARDINO' then '01.540.533/0001-29'
		when ai.HotelEid='ECO' then '01.540.533/0001-29'
		when ai.HotelEid='BRISA' then '00.866.577/0001-80'
		when ai.HotelEid='TERRA' then '00.866.577/0001-80'
		when ai.HotelEid='MAR' then '00.866.577/0001-80'
		when ai.HotelEid='SOL' then '00.866.577/0001-80'
		when ai.HotelEid='AGUA' then '00.866.577/0001-80'
		when ai.HotelEid='POUSADAS' then '00.866.577/0001-80'
	end as cnpj,
	'MULTIVENDAS' as sistemaOrigem,
	am.AccountNumber as numeroConta,
	ct.code as numCartao,
	am.MovementNumber,
	am.MovementDate as dataMovimentacao,

	case 
		when am.Origin=0 and s.SaleNumber is not null then 'Venda'
		when am.Origin=0 and co.CashNumber is not null then 'Pagamento'
		when am.Origin=0 and am.RelatedMovementNumber is not null then 'Estorno'
		when am.Origin=127 and av.VoucherNumber is not null then 'Crdito Voucher Opera'
		when am.Origin=1 then 'Recarga de Crdito'
		when am.Origin=2 and am.TransferMovementNumber is not null then 'Transferencia'
		when am.Origin=2 and am.TransferMovementNumber is null then 'Devoluo de Crdito'
		when am.Origin=3 then 'Pagamento de fatura MultiClubes'
		when am.Origin=4 then 'Desconto por carto danificado'
		when am.Origin=5 then 'Crdito no devolvido'
		when am.Origin=6 then 'Recarga de crditos MultiClubes'
		when am.Origin=7 then 'Crdito inicial na ativao de carto com valor de face'
		when am.Origin=8 then 'Custo do carto na ativao'
		when am.Origin=9 then 'Consumo, venda paga pelo MultiClubes'
		when am.Origin=10 then 'Crdito Voucher'
		when am.Origin=11 then 'Voucher no devolvido'
		when am.Origin=12 then 'Devoluo de crditos feita no MultiClubes'
		when am.Origin=13 then 'Consumo de produto voucher'
		when am.Origin=14 then 'Crdito inserido como um Voucher pelo MultiClubes'
		when am.Origin=15 then 'Cobranas lanadas na integrao com Hotel'
		else cast(am.Origin as varchar)
	end as tipoMovimentacao,
	isnull(isnull(usM.name,usS.name),usc.name) as usuario,
	pm.name as formaPagamento,
	isnull(av.value,am.Value) as valor,
	isnull(isnull(co.CashNumber,s.SaleNumber),msi.id) as transacaoOrigem,
	am.RelatedMovementNumber as movimentoOrigem,
	case am.IsReversed 
		when 0 then 'N'
		when 1 then 'S'
	end as flgEstorno,
	case 
		when am.TransferMovementType is not null then 'S'
		else 'N'
	end as flgTransferido,
	am.TransferMovementNumber as numeroMovimentoTransferencia,
	case am.transferMovementType
		when -1 then ct.code
		when 1 then amt.code
	end as numCartaoOrigem,
	case am.transferMovementType
		when -1 then amt.code
		when 1 then ct.code
	end as numCartaoDestino,
	av.VoucherNumber,
	case 
		when co.CashNumber is not null then 'R'
		when s.SaleNumber is not null then 'V'
		when msi.id is not null then 'C'
		else 'M'
	end as tipoTransacaoOrigem
from

	join Accounts a on am.AccountNumber=a.AccountNumber
	left join AccountsInfo ai on a.AccountInfo=ai.id
	join Paymodes pm on am.PayMode=pm.id
	left join 
	(select du.accountnumber,du.code,du.LegacyCode
		from DayUserCards du
	union all
	select du.accountnumber,du.code,du.LegacyCode
		from customers du) ct on am.AccountNumber=ct.AccountNumber
	left join sales s on am.OperationUid=s.SaleUid
	left join 
	(select am.MovementNumber,ct.code from
		AccountMovements am
		left join 
		(select du.accountnumber,du.code
			from DayUserCards du
		union all
		select du.accountnumber,du.code
			from customers du) ct on am.AccountNumber=ct.AccountNumber) amt on amt.MovementNumber=am.TransferMovementNumber
	left join CashOperations co on am.OperationUid=co.OperationUid
	left join users usM on am.AcceptManager=usM.id
	left join users usS on s.[User]=uss.id
	left join users usC on co.[User]=usc.id
	left join Cashes css on s.CashNumber=css.CashNumber
	left join users ops on css.OpeningUser=ops.Id
	left join shops shs on css.Shop=shs.Id
	left join shops es on shs.Root=es.Id
	left join Cashes cso on co.CashNumber=cso.CashNumber
	left join users opo on cso.OpeningUser=opo.Id
	left join shops sho on cso.Shop=sho.Id
	left join shops eo on sho.Root=eo.Id
	left join AccountVouchers av on am.MovementNumber=av.AcquireMovementNumber
	left join Multiclubes.dbo.Members m on ct.legacyCode=m.id
	left join MultiClubes.dbo.titles t on m.Title=t.Id
	left join MultiClubes.dbo.Clubs cl on t.Club=cl.id
	left join Multiclubes.dbo.SaleItems msi on am.MovementNumber=msi.ConsumptionMovement
WHERE
	am.MovementDate>=cast(getdate()-1 as date)

View v_recebimentosMultivendasEN
Query
 
CREATE view ${schemaName}.${viewName} as
select * from
(
select 
	e.Cnpj,
	'MULTIVENDAS' as sistemaOrigem,
	CONCAT(CONCAT(sp.SaleNumber,'-'),sp.PaymentNumber) as idPagamento,
	null as pagamentoUid,
	s.ClosingDateTime as datahora,
	cs.MovementDate,
	pm.Name as formaPagamento,
	sp.ReceivedValue- isnull(sp.ChangeValue,0) as valor,
	null as tipoOperacao,
	op.Name as operador,
	cf.Name as ConferenciaCaixa,
	sh.name as Loja,
	du.accountnumber as NumConta,
	tt.id as idTransacaoTef,
	tt.CardType as Bandeira,
	isnull(tt.ParcelQty,0) as QtdParcelas,
	tt.CardNumber as numCartao,
	tt.Nsu,
	tt.AuthNumber as autorizacao,
	tt.CanceledTefTransaction as idTransacaoTefCancelada,
	'' as tipoMovimentacao,
	null as dataMovimentacao,
	'' as operadorMovimentacao,
	'' as motivoMovimentacao,
	right(replicate('0',33) + cast(isnull(tt.id,0) as varchar),33) as identificadorUnico
From 
	SalePayments sp
	join Paymodes pm on sp.PayMode=pm.Id
	join sales s on sp.SaleNumber=s.SaleNumber
	join Cashes cs on s.CashNumber=cs.CashNumber
	join users op on cs.OpeningUser=op.Id
	join shops sh on cs.Shop=sh.Id
	join shops e on sh.Root=e.Id
	left join users cf on cs.ConferenceUser=cf.Id
	left join AccountMovements am on s.SaleUid=am.OperationUid
	left join
	(select du.accountnumber,du.code
		from DayUserCards du
	union all
	select du.accountnumber,du.code
		from customers du) du on am.AccountNumber=du.AccountNumber
	left join MultiVendas.dbo.TefTransactions tt on tt.SourceNumber=sp.SaleNumber and tt.PaymentNumber=sp.PaymentNumber and tt.SourceType =0
where
	pm.code<>5
union all
select distinct
	e.Cnpj,
	'MULTIVENDAS' as sistemaOrigem,
	cast(co.CashNumber as varchar)as idPagamento,
	co.OperationUid as PagamentoUid,
	co.datetime as datahora,
	cs.MovementDate,
	pm.Name as formaPagamento,
	case
		when co.OperationType=5 then (co.ReceivedValue-isnull(co.ChangeValue,0))*-1
		else co.ReceivedValue-isnull(co.ChangeValue,0)
	end as valor,
	case co.OperationType
		when 5 then 'Devoluo de crdito'
		when 3 then 'Sangria'
		else ''
	end as tipoOperao,
	op.Name as operador,
	cf.Name as ConferenciaCaixa,
	sh.name as Loja,
	du.accountnumber as NumConta,
	tt.id as idTransacaoTef,
	tt.CardType as Bandeira,
	isnull(tt.ParcelQty,0) as QtdParcelas,
	tt.CardNumber as numCartao,
	tt.Nsu,
	tt.AuthNumber as autorizacao,
	tt.CanceledTefTransaction as idTransacaoTefCancelada,
	case 
		when  co.Cancellation is not null then 'Cancelamento de pagamento'
		when  co.CanceledManager is not null and co.Cancellation is null then 'Estorno de pagamento'
	end as tipoMovimentacao,
	case 
		when  co.Cancellation is not null then cas.[DateTime]
		when  co.CanceledManager is not null and co.Cancellation is null then co.datetime
	end as	dataMovimentacao,	
--	cas.[DateTime] as dataMovimentacao,
	usc.name as operadorMovimentacao,
	cr.name as motivoMovimentacao,
	right(replicate('0',33) + cast(isnull(tt.id,0) as varchar),33) as identificadorUnico
From 
	multivendas.dbo.CashOperations co
	join Paymodes pm on co.PayMode=pm.Id
	join Cashes cs on co.CashNumber=cs.CashNumber
	join users op on cs.OpeningUser=op.Id
	join shops sh on cs.Shop=sh.Id
	join shops e on sh.Root=e.Id
	left join MultiVendas.dbo.TefTransactions tt on tt.SourceNumber=co.OperationNumber and tt.SourceType =1
	left join users cf on cs.ConferenceUser=cf.Id
	left join AccountMovements am on co.OperationUid=am.OperationUid
	left join
	(select du.accountnumber,du.code
		from DayUserCards du
	union all
	select du.accountnumber,du.code
		from customers du) du on am.AccountNumber=du.AccountNumber
	left join Cancellations cas on co.Cancellation=cas.Id
	left join users usc on co.CanceledManager=usc.id
	left join CancelReasons cr on cas.Reason=cr.Id
where
		pm.code<>5)a
where
	cast(datahora as date)>=cast(getdate()-1 as date) or 
	cast(dataMovimentacao as date)>=cast(getdate()-1 as date)

View v_transacoestef
Query
 
CREATE view ${schemaName}.${viewName} as
select	
		null as idIntegracaocar,
		tt.datetime as datahora,
		case
			when tt.canceledTefTransaction is null then 'Pagamento'
			when tt.canceledTefTransaction is not null then 'Cancelamento'
		end as Transacao,
		tt.PaymentType as Pagamento,
		--AuthInstitution as Adquirente,
		tt.CardType as Bandeira,
		case
			when tt.sourceType=0 then 'Sitef'--'Consumo PDV'
			when tt.sourceType=1 then 'Sitef'--'Recarga/Pagamento PDV'
			when tt.sourceType=3 then 'Sitef'--'Central de Atendimento Multiclubes'
			when tt.sourceType=4 then 'E-comerce'--'Pagamento Online'
			when tt.sourceType=5 then 'E-comerce'--'Portal'
			when tt.sourceType=6 then 'Sitef'--'AutoAtendimento'
		end as MCorigem,	
		--ParcelType as Parcelamento,
		isnull(tt.ParcelQty,1) as Parcelas,
		tt.CardNumber as Cartao,
		tt.nsu,
		tt.authNumber as autorizacao,
		value as valor,
		'INTEGRAO' as usuarioAD,
		null as coddocumentocm
	from 
		MultiVendas.dbo.TefTransactions tt
	where
		cast(tt.DateTime as date)=dateadd(day,-1,cast(getdate () as date)) and 
		tt.CanceledTefTransaction is null and
		not exists(select 1 
						from 
							MultiVendas.dbo.TefTransactions tt2 
						where 
							tt.id=tt2.CanceledTefTransaction and 
							cast(tt.DateTime as date)=cast(tt2.DateTime as date))

CREATE view v_updtVendasPdvEN as

		e.Cnpj,

		si.ItemNumber,
		case
			when si.reversalOperationNumber is null then 'N'
			else 'S'
		end as flgEstorno,
		case
			when (s.Cancellation is not null and cr.[Type]=0) or s.CanceledManager is not null  then 'S'
			when (si.Cancellation is not null and cr.[Type]=0) or si.CancelManager is not null then 'S'
			else 'N'
		end as flgCancelado,
		case 
			when cr.[Type]=0 and s.Cancellation is not null then 'Cancelamento de venda'
			when cr.[Type]=0 and si.Cancellation is not null then 'Cancelamento de item'
			when cr.[Type]=1 and s.Cancellation is not null then 'Transferencia de venda'
			when cr.[Type]=1 and si.Cancellation is not null then 'Transferencia de venda'
		end as tipoMovimentacao,
		cas.[DateTime] as dataMovimentacao,
		usc.name as operadorMovimentacao,
		cr.name as motivoMovimentacao
	FROM 
		Cancellations cas
		join users usc on cas.CancelManager=usc.id
		join Sales s on cas.id=s.Cancellation
		join cashes cs on s.CashNumber=cs.CashNumber
		join shops sh on cs.Shop=sh.Id
		join shops e on sh.Root=e.Id
		left join SaleItems SI on s.SaleNumber=si.SaleNumber
		left join CancelReasons cr on cas.Reason=cr.Id
	WHERE
		s.SaleType <> 4 and
		cast(cas.[DateTime] as date)=cast(getdate()-1 as date)
union all
SELECT distinct
		e.Cnpj,
		'MULTIVENDAS' as sistemaOrigem,
		s.SaleNumber as SaleNumber,
		si.ItemNumber,
		case
			when si.reversalOperationNumber is null then 'N'
			else 'S'
		end as flgEstorno,
		case
			when (s.Cancellation is not null and cr.[Type]=0) or s.CanceledManager is not null  then 'S'
			when (si.Cancellation is not null and cr.[Type]=0) or si.CancelManager is not null then 'S'
			else 'N'
		end as flgCancelado,
		case 
			when cr.[Type]=0 and s.Cancellation is not null then 'Cancelamento de venda'
			when cr.[Type]=0 and si.Cancellation is not null then 'Cancelamento de item'
			when cr.[Type]=1 and s.Cancellation is not null then 'Transferencia de venda'
			when cr.[Type]=1 and si.Cancellation is not null then 'Transferencia de venda'
		end as tipoMovimentacao,
		cas.[DateTime] as dataMovimentacao,
		usc.name as operadorMovimentacao,
		cr.name as motivoMovimentacao
	FROM 
		Cancellations cas
		join users usc on cas.CancelManager=usc.id
		join SaleItems SI on cas.id=si.Cancellation
		join Sales s on s.SaleNumber=si.SaleNumber
		join cashes cs on s.CashNumber=cs.CashNumber
		join shops sh on cs.Shop=sh.Id
		join shops e on sh.Root=e.Id
		left join CancelReasons cr on cas.Reason=cr.Id
	WHERE
		s.SaleType <> 4 and
		cast(cas.[DateTime] as date)=cast(getdate()-1 as date)

CREATE view ${schemaName}.${viewName} as

			when '7' then 'Servio'
			else cast(p.ProductType as char(1))
		end as TipoProduto,
		isnull(p.LegacyCode,p.MainBarcode) as CodigoProduto,
		p.Name as descricaoProduto,
		t.Percentage as Aliquota,
		p.Ncm,
		p.Cest,
		p.Cfop,
		si.Quantity as quantidade,
		si.UnitPrice as valorUnitario,
		si.SubTotal as subtotal,
		isnull(sii.Value,0) as Acrescimo,
		si.SubTotal+isnull(sii.Value,0) as valorTotal,
		isnull(si.RatedDiscount,0) as desconto,
		case
			when si.reversalOperationNumber is null then 'N'
			else 'S'
		end as flgEstorno,
		case
			when (s.Cancellation is not null and cr.[Type]=0) or s.CanceledManager is not null  then 'S'
			when (si.Cancellation is not null and cr.[Type]=0) or si.CancelManager is not null then 'S'
			else 'N'
		end as flgCancelado,
		case 
			when cr.[Type]=0 and s.Cancellation is not null then 'Cancelamento de venda'
			when cr.[Type]=0 and si.Cancellation is not null then 'Cancelamento de item'
			when cr.[Type]=1 and s.Cancellation is not null then 'Transferencia de venda'
			when cr.[Type]=1 and si.Cancellation is not null then 'Transferencia de venda'
		end as tipoMovimentacao,
		cas.[DateTime] as dataMovimentacao,
		usc.name as operadorMovimentacao,
		cr.name as motivoMovimentacao,
		sh.id as idLoja
	FROM 
		Sales s 
		join SaleItems SI on s.SaleNumber=si.SaleNumber
		join products p on si.Product=p.id
		join Categories c on p.category=c.id
		join cashes cs on s.CashNumber=cs.CashNumber
		join shops sh on cs.Shop=sh.Id
		join shops e on sh.Root=e.Id
		join users us on s.[User]=us.Id
		left Join Categories c1 on c.parent=c1.id
		left join categories c2 on c1.parent=c2.id
		left join Taxations t on p.Taxation=t.id
		left join SaleItemIncreaseCharges sii on si.SaleNumber=sii.SaleNumber and si.ItemNumber=sii.ItemNumber
		left join Cancellations cas on isnull(si.Cancellation,s.Cancellation)=cas.Id
		left join users usc on isnull(cas.CancelManager,isnull(si.CancelManager,s.CanceledManager))=usc.id
		left join CancelReasons cr on cas.Reason=cr.Id
	WHERE
		s.SaleType <> 4 and
		(cast(s.ClosingDateTime as date) >= cast(getdate()-1 as date) or
		cast(cas.[DateTime] as date)>=cast(getdate()-1 as date))
IdxColumn NameData Type
  Cnpj nvarchar

Functions
GetConsumptionReport 
/*
Funo utilizada pelo indicador de desempenho do MultiClubes
*/
CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[GetConsumptionReport](@initialDate DateTime, @finalDate DateTime) 
RETURNS TABLE
AS 
RETURN
(
	SELECT
		Shop.id ID,
		Shop.Name Shop,
		SUM(Sale.Total) Total
	FROM
		Shops Shop
		LEFT JOIN
		(
			SELECT
				Shop.ID ShopID,
				Shop.node Node,
				Sale.total Total
			FROM
				Sales Sale
				JOIN Cashes Cash ON Sale.CashNumber = Cash.CashNumber
				JOIN Shops Shop ON Cash.Shop = Shop.id
			WHERE
				Sale.CanceledManager IS NULL 
				AND Cash.MovementDate BETWEEN @initialDate AND @finalDate
		) AS Sale ON (Shop.id = Sale.ShopID OR Sale.Node LIKE Shop.node + '.%')
	WHERE
		Shop.Parent IS NULL
	GROUP BY
		Shop.id,
		Shop.name
)
GetRechargeReport 
/*
Funo utilizada pelo indicador de desempenho do MultiClubes
*/
CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[GetRechargeReport](@initialDate DateTime, @finalDate DateTime) 
RETURNS TABLE
AS 
RETURN
(
	SELECT
		PayMode.name AS PayMode,
		SUM(value) AS Total
	FROM
		Paymodes PayMode LEFT JOIN
		AccountMovements Movement ON Movement.PayMode = PayMode.id
	WHERE
		--MovementType = 0 pega apenas movimentos (no estornos ou transferncias)
		Movement.MovementType = 0 AND
		--origin IN (1,7) pega apenas Recarga e Ativao de carto
		Movement.origin IN (1, 7) AND 
		--no pega movimentos estornados
		Movement.IsReversed = 0 AND
		
		Movement.MovementDate BETWEEN @initialDate AND @finalDate
	GROUP BY
		PayMode.name
)
