Split 
/*
	Developer: Mauro Couto
	Description: Incluir Stored Procedure que realiza o split de campos que armazenam dados concatenados.
*/
CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[Split](@String nvarchar(4000), @Delimiter char(1))
RETURNS @Results TABLE (ITEM nvarchar(4000))
AS
BEGIN
	DECLARE @Index INT
	DECLARE @Slice nvarchar(4000)
	IF @String IS NULL RETURN
    --  necessrio definir 1 para no ser igual a zero na primeira iterao do loop.
	SET @Index = 1
	WHILE @Index !=0
	BEGIN
		-- Recupera o ndice da primeira ocorrncia do delimitador.
		SELECT @Index = CHARINDEX(@Delimiter, @String)
		-- Copia tudo a esqueda do delimitador para a varivel temporria.
		IF @Index !=0
			SELECT @Slice = LEFT(@String, @Index - 1)
		ELSE
			SELECT @Slice = @String
		-- Adiciona a varivel temporria a tabela de resultado.
		INSERT INTO @Results(ITEM) VALUES(@Slice)
		-- Retira o item adicionado do texto principal.
		SELECT @String = RIGHT(@String, LEN(@String) - @Index)
		-- Interrompe o loop se no restar mais valores no texto principal.
		IF LEN(@String) = 0 BREAK
	END
	RETURN
END
Unmask 
--Vincius Saide
--Altera funo Unmask para permitir que seja vinculada a uma coluna como campo calculado
CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[Unmask](@Temp NVARCHAR(1000))
Returns NVARCHAR(1000)
with schemabinding
AS
BEGIN
    DECLARE @KeepValues AS NVARCHAR(50)
    SET @KeepValues = '%[^a-zA-Z0-9]%'	
    While PATINDEX(@KeepValues, @Temp) > 0
        Set @Temp = Stuff(@Temp, PatIndex(@KeepValues, @Temp), 1, '')
    Return @Temp
END


Procedures
ActivateConsumptionCard 
/*
 *
 * Ativa o carto de consumo definindo limite de crdito e senha.
 * Ainda atualiza/inclui no MultiVendas os dados do scio, ttulo e tipo de ttulo relacionados ao scio descrito no parmetro @memberId ;
 * 
 * Obs:
 * Os dependentes relacionados a um ttulo no so includos nesta atualizao. Deve-se chamar esta procedure para cada scio a ser ativado/bloqueado.
 * Os dados sero atualizados a partir da base do MultiClubes; Certifique que o Cdigo de barras estar atualizado na tabela antes de chamar a procedure.
 * 
 * Parmetros:
 * 
 * @memberId : Id do MultiClubes do scio a ser processado
 * @barcode : Cdigo de barras a ser atribudo
 * @creditLimit: Limite de crdito para carto ps-pago. NULL para carto pr-pago. Parmetro ignorado quando @isAtive = 0
 * @password: senha do carto ou NULL para sem senha. A senha deve ser numrica, com 4 dgitos, regra no tratada pela procedure. Parmetro ignorado quando @isActive = 0
 * @allowLimitIncrease: Indica se o limite de crdito do ttulo poder ser aumentado para comportar o limite definido para o carto de consumo
 * 
 */
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[ActivateConsumptionCard](@memberId INT, @barcode NVARCHAR(30) = NULL, @creditLimit DECIMAL(18,2) = NULL, @password NVARCHAR(30) = NULL, @allowLimitIncrease BIT)
AS
BEGIN	
	
	DECLARE @message NVARCHAR(128)
	-- validando a sequencia do cdigo de barras
	DECLARE @sequenceId INT
	DECLARE @enabled BIT
	DECLARE @sequenceType TINYINT
	DECLARE @creditMode TINYINT
	DECLARE @faceValue DECIMAL(18,2)
	DECLARE @newRefundableBalance DECIMAL(18,2)
	--VALIDANDO SE CARTO J EST ATIVADO PARA SCIO
	if (EXISTS(SELECT * FROM Customers WHERE code = @barcode AND LegacyCode <> CAST(@memberId AS NVARCHAR(30))))
	BEGIN
		SET @message = 'Carto de consumo j ativado'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		return
	END
	--VALIDANDO SE CARTO J EST ATIVADO PARA ANIMAL
	if (EXISTS(SELECT * FROM Animals WHERE code = @barcode))
	BEGIN
		SET @message = 'Carto de consumo j ativado'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		return
	END
	--VALIDANDO SEQUENCIA
	if (ISNUMERIC(@barcode) = 1)
	BEGIN
		DECLARE @cardNumber BIGINT
		SET @cardNumber = CAST(@barcode AS BIGINT)
		exec ValidateCardSequence @cardNumber, @sequenceId OUTPUT, @enabled OUTPUT, @sequenceType OUTPUT, @creditMode OUTPUT, @faceValue OUTPUT
		-- Validao da sequencia
		IF (@sequenceId IS NULL)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Cdigo no autorizado'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		END
		IF (@enabled = 0)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Cdigo no autorizado'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		END
		
		-- SequenceType = 0 All, 1 DayUser, 2 Customer
		IF (@sequenceType <> 0 AND @sequenceType <> 2)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Cdigo no autorizado para cartes de clientes'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		END
		
		-- CreditMode = 0 All, 1 PrePaid, 2 PosPaid, 3 FaceValue
		IF (@creditMode = 1 AND @creditLimit > 0)
		BEGIN
		
			--VALIDANDO carto PREPAGO
			SET @message = 'Cdigo no autorizado para cartes de ps-pago'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		
		END
		ELSE IF (@creditMode = 3)
		BEGIN
			--VALIDANDO carto COM VALOR DE FACE
			SET @message = 'No  permitido ativao de scios com carto com valor de face'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		END
		--VALIDANDO carto j ATIVADO PARA DayUser
		IF (EXISTS(SELECT * FROM DayUserCards WHERE code = @cardNumber AND DeactivationDate IS NULL))
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Carto de consumo j ativado'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		END
		--VALIDANDO carto PERDIDO OU DANIFICADO
		IF (EXISTS(SELECT * FROM DayUserCards WHERE code = @cardNumber AND DamagedCard = 1))
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Carto de consumo registrado como PERDIDO ou DANIFICADO.'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		END
	END
	
	-- CONFIGURA O carto DE CONSUMO
	DECLARE @accountCustomerId INT
	EXEC @accountCustomerId = dbo.ConfigureConsumptionCardCreditLimit @memberId, @creditLimit, @allowLimitIncrease
	IF (@@ERROR <> 0) RETURN
	-- ALTERA A SENHA DA CONTA DE CONSUMO
	UPDATE 
		Accounts
	SET
		[password] = @password,
		MaxValueWithoutPwd = null
	FROM
		Accounts
		JOIN Customers ON Customers.AccountNumber = Accounts.AccountNumber
	WHERE
		Customers.id = @accountCustomerId
		
	-- ALTERA OS DADOS DO CLIENTE
	UPDATE 
		Customers
	SET
		code = @barcode,
		UsePwdOnlyForManualInput = 0,
		AllowManualNumberInput = 0
	WHERE
		id = @accountCustomerId	

	-- CASO HAJA ALGUM CLIENTE UTILIZANDO O MESMO CDIGO DE BARRAS
	-- ATRIBUDO AGORA, ESTE CDIGO SER ZERADO NA BASE DO MV
	UPDATE 
		Customers 
	SET 
		code = NULL
	WHERE 
		code = @barcode 
		AND id <> @accountCustomerId
END
ActivateDayUserConsumptionCard 
/*
 *
 * Ativa o carto de consumo DayUser definindo limite de crdito e senha.
 * 
 * Parmetros:
 * 
 * @visitorID : ID do visitante
 * @cardNumber : Nmero do carto de consumo
 * @creditLimit: Limite de crdito para carto ps-pago. NULL para carto pr-pago.
 * @password: senha do carto ou NULL para sem senha. A senha deve ser numrica, com 4 dgitos, regra no tratada pela procedure.
 * @promoter : ID do promotor para agrupamento dos consumos
 * @activated : Retorna 1 se o carto for ativado; 0 caso tenha apenas sido atualizado
 */
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[ActivateDayUserConsumptionCard](@visitorID INT, @cardNumber BIGINT, @creditLimit DECIMAL(18,2) = NULL, @password NVARCHAR(30) = NULL, @promoter int = NULL, @autoCreditLimit BIT = 0, @validateOnly BIT = 0, @activated BIT OUTPUT)
AS
BEGIN
	DECLARE @message NVARCHAR(255)
	DECLARE @sequenceId INT
	DECLARE @enabled BIT
	DECLARE @sequenceType TINYINT
	DECLARE @creditMode TINYINT
	DECLARE @faceValue DECIMAL(18,2)
	DECLARE @refundableBalance DECIMAL(18,2)
	SET @activated = 0
	EXEC ValidateCardSequence @cardNumber, @sequenceId OUTPUT, @enabled OUTPUT, @sequenceType OUTPUT, @creditMode OUTPUT, @faceValue OUTPUT
	-- Validao da sequencia
	if (@sequenceId IS NULL OR @enabled = 0)
	BEGIN
		SET @message = 'Cdigo no autorizado'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		RETURN
	END
	-- SequenceType = 0 All, 1 DayUser, 2 Customer
	
	IF (@sequenceType <> 0 AND @sequenceType <> 1)
	BEGIN
		SET @message = 'Cdigo no autorizado para cartes de DayUser'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		RETURN 0
	END
	DECLARE @accountTypeId INT
	DECLARE @maxCreditLimit DECIMAL(18,2)
	SELECT 
		@accountTypeId = id,
		@maxCreditLimit = COALESCE(CreditLimit, 0) 
	FROM 
		AccountTypes
	WHERE 
		HardName = 'DAY_USER'
	-- se for valor de face, no haver devoluao
	if (@faceValue > 0)
	BEGIN
		SET @refundableBalance = NULL;
	END
	ELSE
	BEGIN
		SET @refundableBalance = 0;
	END
	-- CreditMode = 0 All, 1 Prepaid, 2 PosPaid, 3 FaceValue
	-- Define o limite de crdito automaticamente para o carto
	IF (@autoCreditLimit = 1 AND @creditMode = 2)
	BEGIN
		SET @creditLimit = @maxCreditLimit;
	END
	IF (@creditLimit > 0)
	BEGIN
		IF (@creditMode = 1 OR @creditMode = 3)
		BEGIN
		
			SET @message = 'Cdigo no autorizado para emisso de cartes ps-pago'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN 0
		
		END
		ELSE IF (@creditLimit > @maxCreditLimit)
		BEGIN
		
			SET @message = 'Limite de crdito invlido para cartes DayUser'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN 0
		
		END
		ELSE IF (@visitorID IS NULL AND @autoCreditLimit = 0)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Carto ps pago necessita da identificao do visitante'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN 0
		
		END
	END
	
	-- Visitor ZERO  apenas utilizado em liberao de lote para no validar o visitante nulo
	IF (@visitorID = 0) SET @visitorID = NULL
	
	IF (EXISTS(SELECT * FROM Customers WHERE code = CAST(@cardNumber AS NVARCHAR(30))))
	BEGIN
		SET @message = 'Carto de consumo j ativado para scio'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		RETURN 0
	END
	
	IF (EXISTS(SELECT * FROM Animals WHERE code = CAST(@cardNumber AS NVARCHAR(30))))
	BEGIN
		SET @message = 'Carto de consumo j ativado para animal'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		RETURN 0
	END
	IF (EXISTS(SELECT * FROM DayUserCards WHERE code = @cardNumber AND DamagedCard = 1))
	BEGIN
		SET @message = 'Carto de consumo registrado como PERDIDO ou DANIFICADO'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		RETURN 0
	END
	
	DECLARE @accountNumber INT
	DECLARE @currentVisitorID INT
	DECLARE @currentInvoiceNumber INT
	
	SELECT
		@accountNumber = DayUser.AccountNumber,
		@currentVisitorID = CAST(LegacyCode AS INT),
		@currentInvoiceNumber = Account.CurrentInvoiceNumber
	FROM
		DayUserCards AS DayUser
		JOIN Accounts Account ON DayUser.AccountNumber = Account.AccountNumber
	WHERE
		DayUser.code = @cardNumber AND DayUser.DeactivationDate IS NULL
	
	IF (@accountNumber IS NOT NULL)
	BEGIN
	
		IF (@visitorID IS NULL AND @currentVisitorID IS NOT NULL)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Carto de consumo j ativado para visitante'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN 0
			
		END
		ELSE IF (@visitorID IS NOT NULL AND (@currentVisitorID IS NULL OR @visitorID <> @currentVisitorID))
		BEGIN
		
			SET @message = 'Carto de consumo j ativado'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN 0
		
		END
	
	END
	-- Caso a chamada seja apenas para validao, encerra antes de registrar o carto
	IF (@validateOnly = 1) RETURN 0

	IF (@promoter IS NOT NULL AND @promoter <> 0)
	BEGIN
	
		--SE A REFERENCIA FOR DIFERENTE DA FATURA ATUAL, UMA NOVA FATURA  CRIADA
		IF (NOT EXISTS(SELECT * FROM Invoices WHERE InvoiceNumber=@currentInvoiceNumber AND SourceType=1 AND SourceNumber=@promoter))
		BEGIN
			INSERT INTO Invoices (InitialDate, SourceType, SourceNumber, CreationDate) VALUES (CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 1, @promoter, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP)
			SELECT @currentInvoiceNumber = @@IDENTITY	
		END
	END
	ELSE
	BEGIN
		SET @currentInvoiceNumber = NULL
	END
	DECLARE @customerName NVARCHAR(50)
	DECLARE @document NVARCHAR(30)
	SELECT @customerName = CAST(NAME AS NVARCHAR(50)), @document = CAST(DOCUMENT AS NVARCHAR(30)) FROM McVisitors WHERE ID = @visitorID
	IF (@accountNumber IS NULL)
	BEGIN
	
		SET @activated = 1
	
		INSERT INTO Accounts (CreditLimit, RefundableBalance, CurrentInvoiceNumber, [password], CardType) VALUES (@creditLimit, @refundableBalance, @currentInvoiceNumber, @password, 2)
		SELECT @accountNumber = @@IDENTITY
		INSERT INTO DayUserCards (Sequence, AccountType, code, AccountNumber, ActivationDate, CustomerName, document, FaceValue, LegacyOrigin, LegacyCode, Blocked, IsTicket)
		VALUES (@sequenceId, @accountTypeId, @cardNumber, @accountNumber, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, @customerName, @document, @faceValue, 'MULTICLUBES', CAST(@visitorID AS NVARCHAR(30)), 0, 0)
	
	END
	ELSE
	BEGIN
	
		SET @activated = 0
		UPDATE Accounts SET CreditLimit = @creditLimit, CurrentInvoiceNumber = @currentInvoiceNumber WHERE AccountNumber = @accountNumber
		UPDATE DayUserCards SET CustomerName = @customerName, document = @document WHERE AccountNumber = @accountNumber
	END
	
END
ActivateDayUserConsumptionCards 
-- Ativa um lote de cartes de consumo e faz a carga do valor correspondente ao parmetro @value
-- Dispara erros com mensagens formatadas nos casos de Sequncia no liberada ou Valor de face no correspondente ao valor a ser carregado e se houver cartes j ativados dentro desta sequencia.
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[ActivateDayUserConsumptionCards](@initialSeq bigint, @finalSeq bigint, @value decimal, @promoter int)
AS
BEGIN
	DECLARE @sequenceId INT
	DECLARE @enabled BIT
	DECLARE @sequenceType TINYINT
	DECLARE @creditMode TINYINT
	DECLARE @faceValue DECIMAL(18,2)
	DECLARE @creditLimit decimal(18,4)
	
	SELECT
		@sequenceId = id,
		@enabled = [enabled],
		@sequenceType = SequenceType,
		@creditMode = CreditMode,
		@faceValue = FaceValue
	FROM
		CardSequences
	WHERE
		@initialSeq >= initial AND 
		@finalSeq <= final

	DECLARE @message NVARCHAR(255)
	-- Se a sequencia no existe, 
	-- e no h crdito, no faz a ativao do carto.
	if (@sequenceId IS NULL OR @enabled = 0)
	BEGIN
	
		IF (@value IS NULL OR @value = 0)
		BEGIN
			RETURN
		END
		ELSE
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'O intervalo da numerao dos cartes no est liberado.'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		END
	END
	if (@sequenceType <> 0 AND @sequenceType <> 1)
	BEGIN
		SET @message = 'O intervalo da numerao dos cartes no est autorizado para cartes de DayUser.'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		RETURN
	END
	-- CreditMode = 0 All, 1 PrePaid, 2 PosPaid, 3 FaceValue
	IF (@value > 0)
	BEGIN
		IF (@creditMode = 2)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'O intervalo da numerao dos cartes no est autorizado para emisso de cartes pr-pago.'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		END
		ELSE IF (@creditMode = 3 AND @value <> @faceValue)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'O intervalo da numerao dos cartes no est autorizado para emisso de cartes com o valor de crdito informado.'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN		
		END
		
		SET @creditLimit = NULL
	
	END
	ELSE IF (@value < 0)
	BEGIN
	
		IF (@creditMode = 1 OR @creditMode = 3)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'O intervalo da numerao dos cartes no est autorizado para emisso de cartes ps-pago.'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		END
	
		SET @creditLimit = -1 * @value
		SET @value = NULL
	END
	
	DECLARE @cardNumber bigint
	SET @cardNumber = @initialSeq - 1
	WHILE @cardNumber < @finalSeq
	BEGIN
		
		SET @cardNumber = @cardNumber + 1
		if (EXISTS(SELECT * FROM DayUserCards WHERE code = @cardNumber AND DeactivationDate IS NULL))
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Carto de consumo ' + CAST(@cardNumber AS NVARCHAR(30)) + ' j ativado.'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		END
		if (EXISTS(SELECT * FROM DayUserCards WHERE code = @cardNumber AND DamagedCard = 1))
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Carto de consumo ' + CAST(@cardNumber AS NVARCHAR(30)) + ' registrado como PERDIDO ou DANIFICADO.'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		END
		
		--ATIVA O CARTAO
		DECLARE @activated BIT
		EXEC ActivateDayUserConsumptionCard 0, @cardNumber, @creditLimit, NULL, @promoter, 0, 0, @activated OUT
		
		IF (@value > 0)
		BEGIN
			--FAZ A CARGA CASO SEJA PR-PAGO
			DECLARE @movementNumber int
			exec PerformDayUserRecharge @cardNumber, @value, @movementNumber OUTPUT
		END
		
	END
END
CancelDayUserConsumptionCard 
-- Cancela um carto DayUser deixando-o vlido para ser ativado novamente
-- Dispara erro com mensagem formatada caso o carto possua SALDO diferente de ZERO ou SE HOUVER LANAMENTOS que no seja RECARGA e ESTORNOS correspondentes.
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[CancelDayUserConsumptionCard](@cardNumber BIGINT, @validateMovements BIT = 1, @canceled bit OUTPUT)
AS
BEGIN
	DECLARE @cardId INT
	DECLARE @accountNumber INT
	SET @canceled = 0;
	SELECT
		@cardId=ID,
		@accountNumber=AccountNumber
	FROM
		DayUserCards
	WHERE
		Code = @cardNumber AND DeactivationDate IS NULL
	if (@cardId IS NULL)
	BEGIN
		RETURN 0;		
	END
	DECLARE @message NVARCHAR(125)
	-- Se houver movimentos diferentes de RECARGA, ATIVAO, OU CRDITOS MultiClubes, o carto no pode mais ser cancelado pelo MC
	IF (@validateMovements = 1)
	BEGIN
		IF (EXISTS(SELECT * FROM AccountMovements WHERE AccountNumber = @accountNumber AND origin NOT IN (1,6,7)))
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Carto de consumo j possui movimentos e no pode ser cancelado'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		END
	END
	DECLARE @currentBalance DECIMAL(18,4)
	SELECT @currentBalance = CurrentBalance FROM Accounts WHERE AccountNumber = @accountNumber
	-- Se o SALDO for diferente de ZERO
	if (@currentBalance <> 0)
	BEGIN
		IF (@validateMovements = 1)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Carto de consumo possui saldo e no pode ser cancelado'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		END
		RETURN
	END
	UPDATE DayUserCards SET DeactivationDate = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, DamagedCard=0 WHERE ID = @cardId
	UPDATE Accounts SET LastUpdateDate = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP WHERE AccountNumber=@accountNumber
	SET @canceled=1
	RETURN 1
END
CancelDayUserConsumptionCards 
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[CancelDayUserConsumptionCards](@initialSeq bigint, @finalSeq bigint)
AS
BEGIN
	DECLARE @message NVARCHAR(MAX)
	
	CREATE TABLE #CardsToDelete (AccountNumber INT NOT NULL, InvoiceNumber INT NULL)
	INSERT INTO #CardsToDelete (AccountNumber, InvoiceNumber)
	SELECT DayUser.AccountNumber, Account.CurrentInvoiceNumber AS invoice_number FROM 	
		DayUserCards DayUser JOIN
		Accounts Account ON DayUser.AccountNumber = Account.AccountNumber JOIN
		McCanceledDayUserCards Canceled ON DayUser.code = Canceled.BARCODE
	WHERE
		DayUser.DeactivationDate IS NULL AND
		DayUser.code BETWEEN @initialSeq AND @finalSeq
	IF EXISTS(SELECT
				*
			  FROM 
				AccountMovements Movement JOIN
				#CardsToDelete ON Movement.AccountNumber = #CardsToDelete.AccountNumber
			  WHERE
				(Movement.MovementType <> 0 OR Movement.origin <> 6)
			  )
	BEGIN
		SET @message = 'Existem cartes de consumo com movimentos no intervalo.'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		RETURN
	END
	DELETE 
		DayUser
	FROM
		DayUserCards DayUser JOIN
		#CardsToDelete ON DayUser.AccountNumber = #CardsToDelete.AccountNumber
	DELETE
		Movement
	FROM
		AccountMovements Movement JOIN
		#CardsToDelete ON Movement.AccountNumber = #CardsToDelete.AccountNumber
	DELETE 
		Account
	FROM
		Accounts Account JOIN
		#CardsToDelete ON Account.AccountNumber = #CardsToDelete.AccountNumber
	
	DELETE 
		Invoice
	FROM
		Invoices Invoice JOIN
		#CardsToDelete ON Invoice.InvoiceNumber = #CardsToDelete.InvoiceNumber
	DROP TABLE #CardsToDelete
END
ConfigureConsumptionCardCreditLimit 
/*
 *
 * Configura carto de consumo definindo limite de crdito e senha.
 * 
 * @memberId : Id do MultiClubes do scio a ser processado
 * @creditLimit: Limite de crdito para carto ps-pago. NULL para carto pr-pago. Parmetro ignorado quando @isAtive = 0
 * @allowLimitIncrease: indica se o limite de crdito do ttulo poder ser aumentado para comportar o limite de crdito do carto de consumo
 * 
 */
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[ConfigureConsumptionCardCreditLimit](@memberId INT, @creditLimit DECIMAL(18,2) = NULL, @allowLimitIncrease BIT, @animalId INT = NULL)
AS
BEGIN	
	
	IF (@creditLimit IS NULL) SET @creditLimit = 0
	
	DECLARE @message NVARCHAR(128)
	
	DECLARE @accountCustomerId INT
	IF(@memberId IS NOT NULL)
	BEGIN
		EXEC GetAccountCustomer @memberId, @accountCustomerId OUTPUT
	END
	IF(@animalId IS NOT NULL)
	BEGIN
		EXEC GetAccountAnimal @animalId, @accountCustomerId OUTPUT
	END
	--Validando o limite mximo individual do carto
	DECLARE @MAX_CREDIT_LIMIT decimal(18,2)
	SELECT @MAX_CREDIT_LIMIT = CAST(CAST(value AS NVARCHAR(30)) AS decimal(18,2)) FROM Config WHERE [key] = 'MAX_CREDIT_LIMIT'
	if ((@creditLimit > @MAX_CREDIT_LIMIT) AND @animalId IS NULL)
	BEGIN
		SET @message = 'O limite de crdito excede o valor mximo permitido para o carto de consumo.'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		RETURN
	END
	
	--Validando os limites de crdito
	DECLARE @accountInfoId AS INT
	DECLARE @accountNumber AS INT
	DECLARE @currentBalance AS DECIMAL(18,2)
	DECLARE @maxCreditLimit AS DECIMAL(18,2)
	DECLARE @assignedCreditLimit AS DECIMAL(18,2)
	IF(@memberId IS NOT NULL)
	BEGIN
		SELECT
			@accountInfoId = AccountInfo.id,
			@accountNumber = Account.AccountNumber,
			@currentBalance = Account.CurrentBalance,
			@maxCreditLimit = COALESCE(AccountInfo.MaxCreditLimit, AccountType.CreditLimit, 0),
			@assignedCreditLimit = COALESCE(UsedCreditLimit.Value, 0)
		FROM
			AccountsInfo AS AccountInfo 
			JOIN AccountTypes AS AccountType ON AccountInfo.AccountType = AccountType.id
			JOIN Customers AS Customer ON AccountInfo.id = Customer.AccountInfo
			JOIN Accounts AS Account ON Customer.AccountNumber = Account.AccountNumber	
			OUTER APPLY
			(
				SELECT
					SUM(COALESCE(OtherAccounts.CreditLimit,0)) AS Value
				FROM
					Customers AS OtherCustomers
					JOIN Accounts AS OtherAccounts ON OtherCustomers.AccountNumber = OtherAccounts.AccountNumber
				WHERE
					OtherCustomers.AccountInfo = AccountInfo.id
					AND OtherAccounts.AccountNumber <> Account.AccountNumber
			) AS UsedCreditLimit
		WHERE
			Customer.id = @accountCustomerId
	END
	IF(@animalId IS NOT NULL)
	BEGIN
		SELECT
			@accountNumber = Animals.AccountNumber
		FROM
			Animals
		WHERE
			Animals.id = @accountCustomerId
		-- ALTERA O LIMITE DE CRDITO DA CONTA
		UPDATE 
			Accounts
		SET
			CreditLimit =
			(
				CASE
					WHEN @creditLimit = 0 THEN NULL
					ELSE @creditLimit
				END
			),
			RefundableBalance = ISNULL(RefundableBalance, 0),
			LastUpdateDate = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
		WHERE
			AccountNumber = @accountNumber
		UPDATE Animals SET LastUpdateDate = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP WHERE Id=@accountCustomerId
	END
	ELSE
	BEGIN
	
		--Validando os limites de crdito compartilhado do ttulo
		IF (@allowLimitIncrease = 0)
		BEGIN
	
			IF (@creditLimit + @assignedCreditLimit > @maxCreditLimit)
			BEGIN
				IF (@maxCreditLimit = 0)
				BEGIN
					SET @message = 'O ttulo no permite cartes de consumo ps-pago.'
					RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
					RETURN
				END
				ELSE
				BEGIN
					SET @message = 'O limite de crdito do titular e dependentes excede o limite mximo definido para a conta de consumo.'
					RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
					RETURN
				END
			END
		
		END
		--Validando a reduo de limite abaixo do saldo atual
		IF (@currentBalance < 0 AND (@creditLimit < -1 * @currentBalance))
		BEGIN
	
			SET @message = 'O limite de crdito no pode ser modificado. Efetue o pagamento dos cartes de consumo antes de redefinir o limite de crdito.'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		
		END
		-- ALTERA O LIMITE DE CRDITO DA CONTA
		UPDATE 
			Accounts
		SET
			CreditLimit =
			(
				CASE
					WHEN @creditLimit = 0 THEN NULL
					ELSE @creditLimit
				END
			),
			RefundableBalance = ISNULL(RefundableBalance, 0),
			LastUpdateDate = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
		WHERE
			AccountNumber = @accountNumber

		IF (@creditLimit + @assignedCreditLimit > @maxCreditLimit)
		BEGIN
			UPDATE 
				AccountsInfo 
			SET 
				MaxCreditLimit = @creditLimit + @assignedCreditLimit
			WHERE
				id = @accountInfoId
			
			UPDATE AccountsInfo SET LastUpdateDate = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP WHERE id=@accountInfoId
		END
		UPDATE Customers SET LastUpdateDate = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP WHERE id=@accountCustomerId
	END
	RETURN @accountCustomerId
END
ConfigureConsumptionCardPassword 
/*
 *
 * Configura carto de consumo definindo limite de crdito e senha.
 * Ainda atualiza/inclui no MultiVendas os dados do scio, ttulo e tipo de ttulo relacionados ao scio descrito no parmetro @memberId ;
 * 
 * 
 * @memberId : Id do MultiClubes do scio a ser processado
 * @password: Senha do carto de consumo
 * 
 */
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[ConfigureConsumptionCardPassword](@memberId INT, @password NVARCHAR(256))
AS
BEGIN	
	
	DECLARE @message NVARCHAR(128)
	DECLARE @accountCustomerId INT
	exec GetAccountCustomer @memberId, @accountCustomerId OUTPUT
	-- ALTERA A SENHA DA CONTA DE CONSUMO
	UPDATE 
		Accounts 
	SET
		[password] = @password,
		MaxValueWithoutPwd = null
	FROM
		Accounts 
		JOIN Customers ON Customers.AccountNumber = Accounts.AccountNumber
	WHERE
		Customers.id = @accountCustomerId
	RETURN @accountCustomerId
END
CreateInvoice 
-- Cria a fatura de importao de consumo para scios
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[CreateInvoice](@generation INT, @accountInfoId INT, @initialDate DATETIME, @finalDate DATETIME)
AS
BEGIN
	IF (@accountInfoId IS NULL) RETURN
	IF (NOT EXISTS(SELECT * FROM Invoices WHERE AccountInfo=@accountInfoId AND Generation=@generation))
	BEGIN					         
		
		-- Cria a fatura
		DECLARE @invoiceNumber INT;
		DECLARE @totalInvoiceValue DECIMAL(18,2);
		SET @totalInvoiceValue = 0;
		INSERT INTO Invoices (AccountInfo, Generation, InitialDate, FinalDate, DueDate, TotalValue, CreationDate) VALUES (@accountInfoId, @generation, @initialDate, @finalDate, @finalDate, 0, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) 
		SELECT @invoiceNumber = @@IDENTITY
		
		-- Busca por cada movimento das contas de consumo
		DECLARE @accountNumber INT;
		DECLARE @invoiceValue DECIMAL(18,2);
		DECLARE @currentBalance DECIMAL(18,2);
		DECLARE @previousBalance DECIMAL(18,2);
		DECLARE InvoiceCursor CURSOR FOR
		SELECT
			Accounts.AccountNumber,
			Accounts.CurrentBalance,
			SUM(AccountMovements.Value) 
		FROM
			AccountMovements
			JOIN Accounts ON AccountMovements.AccountNumber=Accounts.AccountNumber
		WHERE
			Accounts.AccountInfo=@accountInfoId AND
			AccountMovements.InvoiceNumber IS NULL AND
			AccountMovements.Origin<>3 AND
			AccountMovements.[DateTime]<=@finalDate
		GROUP BY
			Accounts.AccountNumber,
			Accounts.CurrentBalance
			
		OPEN InvoiceCursor   
		FETCH NEXT FROM InvoiceCursor INTO @accountNumber, @currentBalance, @invoiceValue
		WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0   
		BEGIN   
			-- Se o somatrio do perodo for POSITIVO ou o saldo atual for POSITIVO
			-- no  gerado fatura a cobrar ao cliente.
			IF (@invoiceValue > 0 OR @currentBalance > 0)
			BEGIN
				SET @invoiceValue = 0
			END
			ELSE
			BEGIN
				--Avalia o valor somado no perodo at o limite
				--mximo do saldo atual da conta.
				--
				-- Por exemplo, se o somatrio do perodo  de R$ -10,00
				-- E o cliente possui em conta R$ -8,00
				-- O valor somente poder ser faturado ao limite de R$ -8,00
				if (@currentBalance > @invoiceValue)
				BEGIN
					SET @invoiceValue = @currentBalance
				END				
				
				SET @invoiceValue = @invoiceValue * -1
				
			END		
		
			-- Atualiza os movimentos com a fatura
			UPDATE
				AccountMovements
			SET
				InvoiceNumber=@invoiceNumber
			WHERE
				AccountNumber=@accountNumber AND 
				InvoiceNumber IS NULL AND
				Origin<>3 AND
				[DateTime]<=@finalDate

			-- Retorna o saldo anterior ao primeiro movimento dessa fatura
			-- LEFT JOIN alternativo para a funo SUM(Value) OVER (PARTITION BY AccountNumber ORDER BY MovementNumber)
			-- SUM .. OVER .. ORDER BY no suportado em verses anteriores ao SQL SERVER 2012
			SELECT TOP(1)
				@previousBalance=SUM(b.Value)
			FROM 
				AccountMovements AS a
				LEFT JOIN AccountMovements AS b ON  
				(
					a.MovementNumber>b.MovementNumber
					AND a.AccountNumber=b.AccountNumber
				)
			WHERE
				a.AccountNumber=@accountNumber
				AND a.MovementNumber <= (SELECT MIN(MovementNumber) FROM AccountMovements WHERE AccountNumber=@accountNumber AND InvoiceNumber=@invoiceNumber)
			GROUP BY 
				a.AccountNumber, a.MovementNumber
			ORDER BY 
				a.MovementNumber DESC
			-- Inseri o registro em InvoiceAccounts
			INSERT INTO InvoiceAccounts (InvoiceNumber, AccountNumber, Value, PreviousBalance) VALUES (@invoiceNumber, @accountNumber, @invoiceValue, COALESCE(@previousBalance, 0))
			SET @totalInvoiceValue = @totalInvoiceValue + @invoiceValue;
			FETCH NEXT FROM InvoiceCursor INTO @accountNumber, @currentBalance, @invoiceValue
			
		END
		CLOSE InvoiceCursor   
		DEALLOCATE InvoiceCursor	
		
		UPDATE Invoices SET TotalValue=@totalInvoiceValue WHERE InvoiceNumber=@invoiceNumber	
	END   
END
DeleteConsumptionCard 
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[DeleteConsumptionCard](@memberId INT)
AS
BEGIN	
	
	DECLARE @accountCustomerId INT
	EXEC GetAccountCustomer @memberId, @accountCustomerId OUTPUT, 0
	IF (@accountCustomerId IS NOT NULL)
	BEGIN
		UPDATE
			Accounts
		SET 
			CreditLimit = NULL,
			[password] = NULL,
			MaxValueWithoutPwd = null
		FROM
			Accounts
			JOIN Customers ON Accounts.AccountNumber = Customers.AccountNumber
		WHERE
			Customers.id = @accountCustomerId

		UPDATE
			Customers
		SET
			code = NULL,
			UsePwdOnlyForManualInput = 0,
			AllowManualNumberInput = 0,
			LastUpdateDate = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
		WHERE
			id = @accountCustomerId	
	END
END
DeleteMember 
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[DeleteMember](@memberId INT)
AS
BEGIN	
	SET XACT_ABORT OFF
	DECLARE @deleted INT
	DECLARE @customerId INT
	DECLARE @accountNumber INT
	SELECT
		@customerId = c.id,
		@accountNumber = c.AccountNumber
	FROM
		Customers c,
		AccountsInfo i
	WHERE
		c.AccountInfo = i.id AND
		i.LegacyOrigin = 'MULTICLUBES' AND
		c.LegacyCode = CAST(@memberId AS NVARCHAR(30))
	if (@customerId IS NULL)
	BEGIN
		SET @deleted = 1
	END
	ELSE
	BEGIN
		DECLARE @currentBalance DECIMAL(18,2);
		SELECT 
			@currentBalance = CurrentBalance 
		FROM 
			Accounts 
		WHERE 
			AccountNumber = @accountNumber
		IF (@currentBalance <> 0)
		BEGIN
			DECLARE @message NVARCHAR(255)
			SET @message = 'O scio possui saldo pendente em seu carto de consumo. Liquide os movimentos e tente novamente.'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		END
		DECLARE @tranCount int
		SET @tranCount = @@TRANCOUNT
		IF (@tranCount = 0) BEGIN
			BEGIN TRANSACTION
		END
		ELSE BEGIN
			SAVE TRANSACTION deleteCustomer
		END
	
		DECLARE @error int
		SET @error = 0
		IF (EXISTS(SELECT * FROM Orders WHERE AccountNumber=@accountNumber))
		BEGIN
			SET @error=1
		END
		IF (@error=0 AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT * FROM AccountMovements WHERE AccountNumber=@accountNumber))
		BEGIN
			
			if (@error = 0)
			BEGIN
				DELETE FROM PreSales WHERE AccountNumber=@accountNumber
				SET @error = @@ERROR
			END
			if (@error = 0)
			BEGIN
				UPDATE AccountsInfo SET [OwnerAccount]=NULL WHERE [OwnerAccount]=@accountNumber
				SET @error = @@ERROR
			END
			if (@error = 0)
			BEGIN
				DELETE FROM Customers WHERE [Id] = @customerId
				SET @error = @@ERROR
			END
			if (@error = 0)
			BEGIN
				DELETE FROM Accounts WHERE AccountNumber = @accountNumber
				SET @error = @@ERROR
			END
		END
		ELSE
		BEGIN
			SET @error = 1;
		END
		
		IF (@error = 0)
		BEGIN
		
			IF (@tranCount = 0)
			BEGIN
				COMMIT TRANSACTION
			END
			SET @deleted = 1
		END
		ELSE
		BEGIN
			IF (@tranCount = 0)
			BEGIN
				ROLLBACK TRANSACTION
			END
			ELSE
			BEGIN
				ROLLBACK TRANSACTION deleteCustomer
			END
			
			SET @deleted = 0
			UPDATE Customers SET Code=NULL, [Status]=2 WHERE Id=@customerId
		END
	END
	SET XACT_ABORT ON
	RETURN @deleted
END
GetAccountAnimal 
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[GetAccountAnimal](@mcAnimalId INT, @animalAccountNumber INT OUTPUT, @createNew BIT = 1 OUTPUT)
AS
BEGIN
	DECLARE @message NVARCHAR(MAX)
	DECLARE @mvLegacyUpdateDate DATETIME
	DECLARE @mcLastUpdateDate DATETIME
	DECLARE @mcCurrentBarcode NVARCHAR(30)
	DECLARE @mcCurrentTitleId INT
	DECLARE @mcCurrentMemberTitularId INT
	DECLARE @currentMemberTitularAccountNumber INT
	DECLARE @animalId INT
	DECLARE @titleAccountInfoId INT
	DECLARE @legacyCode NVARCHAR(30)
	DECLARE @maxCreditLimit DECIMAL(18,2)
	SET @legacyCode = CAST(@mcAnimalId AS VARCHAR(30))
	--Consultando dados do animal da base do MultiClubes
	SELECT
		@mcLastUpdateDate=LASTUPDATEDATE,
		@mcCurrentTitleId=TITLE,
		@mcCurrentBarcode=BARCODE
	FROM
		McAnimals
	WHERE
		id=@mcAnimalId
	SELECT
		@mcCurrentMemberTitularId=ID
	FROM
		McMembers
	WHERE
		Title=@mcCurrentTitleId
	-- Validao da sequencia
	IF (@mcCurrentBarcode IS NOT NULL AND ISNUMERIC(@mcCurrentBarcode)=1)
	BEGIN
		DECLARE @sequenceId INT
		DECLARE @enabled BIT
		DECLARE @sequenceType TINYINT
		DECLARE @creditMode TINYINT
		DECLARE @faceValue DECIMAL(18,2)
		EXEC ValidateCardSequence @mcCurrentBarcode, @sequenceId OUTPUT, @enabled OUTPUT, @sequenceType OUTPUT, @creditMode OUTPUT, @faceValue OUTPUT
		-- Validao da sequencia
		IF (@sequenceId IS NULL)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Cdigo no autorizado'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		END
		IF (@enabled = 0)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Cdigo no autorizado'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN
		END
		-- SequenceType = 0 All, 1 DayUser, 2 Customer, 3 Animal
		IF (@sequenceType <> 3)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Cdigo no autorizado para cartes de animais'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN 0
		END
		 -- CreditMode = 0 All, 1 PrePaid, 2 PosPaid, 3 FaceValue
		IF (@creditMode=3)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Cdigo no autorizado para cartes de animais'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			RETURN 0
		END
	END
	--Consultando o animal na base do MultiVendas
    SELECT
		@animalId=id,
	    @mvLegacyUpdateDate=LegacyUpdateDate
    FROM
	    Animals
    WHERE
	    LegacyCode=@legacyCode
    -- Caso o animal nao exista e esteja alocado,  criado
    IF (@animalId IS NULL AND @mcCurrentTitleId IS NOT NULL AND @createNew = 1)
    BEGIN
	   INSERT INTO Animals (LegacyCode, name) 
	   VALUES (@legacyCode, '')
	   
	   SET @animalId = @@IDENTITY
    END
	-- Caso o animal esteja em alguma locao ele pertence ao ttulo daquela locao
	IF(@mcCurrentTitleId IS NOT NULL)
	BEGIN
		--Executando a integrao para recuperar/atualizar/incluir o ttulo
		EXEC GetAccountInfo @mcCurrentTitleId, @titleAccountInfoId OUTPUT
		--Executando a integrao para recuperar/atualizar/incluir o titular pois  essencial para poder encontrar o animal (visualmente)
		EXEC GetAccountCustomer @mcCurrentMemberTitularId, @currentMemberTitularAccountNumber OUTPUT, 1, 0
		SELECT
			 @animalAccountNumber=Accounts.AccountNumber 
		FROM
			 AnimalAccounts
			 JOIN Accounts ON Accounts.AccountNumber=AnimalAccounts.AccountNumber
		WHERE
			 AnimalAccounts.Animal=@animalId
			 AND Accounts.AccountInfo=@titleAccountInfoId
		-- Caso a combinaao titulo-animal ainda nao exista, cria uma nova conta para ele naquele titulo
		IF(@animalAccountNumber IS NULL AND @createNew = 1)
		BEGIN
			 INSERT INTO Accounts (AccountInfo, CardType) VALUES (@titleAccountInfoId, 3)
			 SELECT @animalAccountNumber = @@IDENTITY
			 INSERT INTO AnimalAccounts(Animal, AccountNumber)
			 VALUES (@animalId, @animalAccountNumber)
			 -- CreditMode = 0 All, 1 PrePaid, 2 PosPaid, 3 FaceValue
			 IF (@creditMode<>1)
			 BEGIN
				 SELECT
					@maxCreditLimit=ISNULL(CONVERT(DECIMAL(18,2), Value), 0)
				 FROM
					Config
				 WHERE
					[Key]='ANIMAL_MAX_CREDIT_LIMIT'
				 UPDATE 
					Accounts
				 SET
					CreditLimit = @maxCreditLimit,
					RefundableBalance = ISNULL(RefundableBalance, 0),
					LastUpdateDate = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
				 WHERE
					AccountNumber=@animalAccountNumber
			END
		END
		ELSE
		BEGIN
			SET @createNew=0
		END
		
	END
    IF (@animalId IS NOT NULL)
    BEGIN
		
	   UPDATE Animals
	   SET
		  AccountInfo = @titleAccountInfoId,
		  AccountNumber = @animalAccountNumber,
		  LegacyUpdateDate = @mcLastUpdateDate,
		  code = @mcCurrentBarcode,
		  member = mc.MEMBER,
		  mapLocationName = mc.ANIMALMAPLOCATIONNAME,
		  name = mc.NAME,
		  gender = mc.GENDER,
		  breed = mc.BREED,
		  pelage = mc.PELAGE,
		  BirthDate = mc.BIRTHDATE,
		  PassportNumber = mc.PASSPORTNUMBER,
		  veterinary = mc.VETERINARY,
		  ChipNumber = mc.CHIPNUMBER,
		  [owner] = mc.[OWNER],
		  comments = mc.COMMENTS,
		  [status] = mc.[STATUS],
		  LastUpdateDate = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
	   FROM
		  Animals,
		  McAnimals mc
	   WHERE
		  Animals.LegacyCode=mc.id AND
		  Animals.id = @animalId
    END
	
END
GetAccountCustomer 
-- Ajuste na procedure
-- Carisio
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[GetAccountCustomer](@memberId INT, @accountCustomerId INT OUTPUT, @createNew BIT = 1 OUTPUT, @overrideStatus BIT = 0)
AS
BEGIN
	declare @message NVARCHAR(MAX)
	declare @legacyUpdateDate DateTime
	declare @lastUpdateDate DateTime
	declare @accountInfoId INT
	declare @status int
	declare @accountNumber INT
	declare @code NVARCHAR(30)
	declare @legacyStatus int
	declare @titleId INT
	declare @barcode NVARCHAR(30)
	declare @isTitular bit
	declare @cardType tinyint
	declare @legacyCode NVARCHAR(30)
	SET @legacyCode = CAST(@memberId AS NVARCHAR(30))
	--Consultando dados da base do MultiClubes
	SELECT
		@lastUpdateDate = LastUpdateDate,
		@titleId=Title,
		@isTitular=TITULAR, 
		@barcode=BARCODE,
		@legacyStatus=STATUS,
		@cardType=CARDTYPE
	FROM
		McMembers
	WHERE
		id=@memberId

	-- Validao da sequencia
	IF (@barcode IS NOT NULL AND ISNUMERIC(@barcode)=1)
	BEGIN
		DECLARE @sequenceId INT
		DECLARE @enabled BIT
		DECLARE @sequenceType TINYINT
		DECLARE @creditMode TINYINT
		DECLARE @faceValue DECIMAL(18,2)
		EXEC ValidateCardSequence @barcode, @sequenceId OUTPUT, @enabled OUTPUT, @sequenceType OUTPUT, @creditMode OUTPUT, @faceValue OUTPUT
		if (@sequenceId IS NOT NULL)
		BEGIN
			IF (@enabled = 0)
			BEGIN
				SET @message = 'Cdigo no autorizado'
				RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
				RETURN
			END
			-- SequenceType = 0 All, 1 DayUser, 2 Customer
			IF (@sequenceType <> 0 AND @sequenceType <> 2)
			BEGIN
				SET @message = 'Cdigo no autorizado para cartes de scios'
				RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
				RETURN 0
			END
		END
	END
	--Executando a integrao para recuperar/atualizar/incluir o ttulo
	EXEC GetAccountInfo @titleId, @accountInfoId OUTPUT
	--Consultando dados da base do MultiVendas
	SELECT
		@accountCustomerId=id,
		@legacyUpdateDate=LegacyUpdateDate,
		@status=status,
		@accountNumber = AccountNumber,
		@code = code
	FROM
		Customers
	WHERE
		AccountInfo=@accountInfoId AND
		LegacyCode=@legacyCode 
	IF (@accountCustomerId IS NULL AND @createNew = 1)
	BEGIN
		INSERT INTO Accounts (AccountInfo, CardType) VALUES (@accountInfoId, 1)
		SELECT @accountNumber = @@IDENTITY
		INSERT INTO Customers (AccountInfo,AccountNumber,code,LegacyCode, name)
		VALUES (@accountInfoId, @accountNumber, @barcode, @legacyCode, '')
		SELECT @accountCustomerId = @@IDENTITY
		SET @code = @barcode
	END
	ELSE
	BEGIN
		SET @createNew = 0
	END
	IF (
			(@overrideStatus = 1)
			OR
			(
				(@accountCustomerId IS NOT NULL) 
				AND 
				(@legacyUpdateDate IS NULL OR @lastUpdateDate > @legacyUpdateDate)
			)
		)
	BEGIN
		if (@isTitular = 1)
		BEGIN
			UPDATE AccountsInfo set OwnerAccount=@accountNumber WHERE id=@accountInfoId
		END
		ELSE
		BEGIN
			-- Se o membro nao for o titular no MC, mas no MV estiver definido como titular,
			-- o ID do titular  zerado no MV.
			DECLARE @ownerAccount INT
			SELECT @ownerAccount = OwnerAccount FROM AccountsInfo where id = @accountInfoId
			if (@ownerAccount = @accountNumber)
			BEGIN
				UPDATE AccountsInfo SET OwnerAccount=NULL WHERE id=@accountInfoId
			END
		END
		/*
		 * Se no MultiVendas o cliente estiver bloqueado, assim ficar independente do status no MultiClubes
		 * De outra forma, ficar o status do MultiClubes
		 */
		IF (@overrideStatus = 1 OR @status IS NULL OR @status <> 4)
		BEGIN
			SET @status = @legacyStatus
		END
		UPDATE Customers
		SET
			LegacyUpdateDate = @lastUpdateDate,
			Status = @status,
			Code=@barcode,
			Name = McMembers.Name,
			Sex = McMembers.Sex,
			CivilStatus = McMembers.CivilStatus,
			BirthDate = McMembers.BirthDate,
			Rg = McMembers.Rg,
			Cpf = McMembers.Document,
			Email = McMembers.Email,
			MobilePhone = McMembers.MobilePhone
		FROM
			Customers
			JOIN McMembers ON Customers.LegacyCode=CAST(McMembers.ID AS NVARCHAR)
		WHERE
			Customers.id = @accountCustomerId
		-- Se o carto no  mais carto de consumo
		-- OU se o Cdigo de barras vindo do MultiClubes estiver NULO
		-- As informaes de SENHA e LIMITE so zeradas do MultiVendas
		if (@cardType <> 2)
		BEGIN
			UPDATE 
				Customers
			SET 
				Code = NULL
			WHERE 
				Id = @accountCustomerId
			UPDATE 
				Accounts
			SET 
				CreditLimit = NULL, [password] = NULL, [MaxValueWithoutPwd] = NULL
			WHERE 
				AccountNumber = @accountNumber
		END
		UPDATE Customers SET LastUpdateDate = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP WHERE Id=@accountCustomerId	
	END
END
GetAccountInfo 
-- Ajuste na procedure
-- Carisio
/* Inclui/Atualiza os dados do TTULO do MultiVendas a partir do ID do titulo do MultiClubes
 */
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[GetAccountInfo](@titleId INT, @accountInfoId INT OUTPUT, @createNew bit = 1)
AS
BEGIN	
	DECLARE @legacyUpdateDate DATETIME
	DECLARE @lastUpdateDate DATETIME
	DECLARE @accountTypeId INT
	DECLARE @currentAccountTypeId INT
	DECLARE @titleTypeId INT
	DECLARE @goldCard NVARCHAR(50)
	
	DECLARE @legacyCode NVARCHAR(30)
	SET @legacyCode = CAST(@titleId AS NVARCHAR(30))
	SELECT 
		@accountInfoId=id, 
		@legacyUpdateDate=LegacyUpdateDate, 
		@currentAccountTypeId=AccountType 
	FROM 
		AccountsInfo
	WHERE
		LegacyOrigin='MULTICLUBES' 
		AND LegacyCode = @legacyCode 
		
	SELECT 
		@lastUpdateDate = LastUpdateDate, 
		@titleTypeId=TitleType, 
		@goldCard = GoldCard
	FROM 
		McTitles 
	WHERE
		id=@titleId
	-- VERIFICA O TIPO DE CLIENTE
	
	SELECT @accountTypeId = AccountType FROM AccountTypeCorrespondents WHERE McTitleType = @titleTypeId
	IF (@accountTypeId IS NULL)
	BEGIN
	
		DECLARE @isMember BIT
		SELECT @isMember = MEMBER FROM McTitleTypes WHERE ID = @titleTypeId
		IF (@isMember = 1)
		BEGIN
		
			IF (@goldCard IS NULL OR @goldCard = '')
			BEGIN
				SELECT @accountTypeId = id FROM AccountTypes WHERE HardName = 'MEMBER'
			END
			ELSE
			BEGIN
				SELECT @accountTypeId = id FROM AccountTypes WHERE HardName = 'GOLD'
			END
		
		END
		ELSE
		BEGIN
			
			SELECT @accountTypeId = id FROM AccountTypes WHERE HardName = 'DAY_USER'
			
		END
	
	END
	
	IF (@accountInfoId IS NULL AND @createNew = 1)
	BEGIN
		INSERT INTO AccountsInfo (AccountType,status,LegacyOrigin,LegacyCode,MaxCreditLimit)
		VALUES (@accountTypeId, 0, 'MULTICLUBES', @legacyCode,NULL)
		SELECT @accountInfoId= @@IDENTITY
	END
	--Atualiza o cliente caso a data de lastUpdate tenha sido alterada ou caso o a regra de tipo de cliente tenha mudado.
	IF ((@accountInfoId IS NOT NULL) AND (@legacyUpdateDate IS NULL OR @lastUpdateDate > @legacyUpdateDate OR @currentAccountTypeId <> @accountTypeId))
	BEGIN
		UPDATE AccountsInfo
		SET
			AccountsInfo.LegacyUpdateDate=@lastUpdateDate,
			AccountsInfo.AccountType=@accountTypeId,
			AccountsInfo.code=mc.CODE,
			AccountsInfo.status=mc.STATUS
		FROM
			AccountsInfo
			JOIN McTitles mc ON 
			(
				AccountsInfo.LegacyOrigin='MULTICLUBES' AND
				AccountsInfo.LegacyCode=CAST(mc.id AS NVARCHAR)
			)
		WHERE
			AccountsInfo.id=@accountInfoId
	END
END
PerformDayUserRecharge 
-- Efetua recarga de crditos no carto DayUser
-- Parmetro de retorno @movementUid deve ser utilizado em caso de estorno
-- Dispara erros com mensagem formatadas nos casos de carto de consumo no ativado e carto de consumo com valor de face j carregado
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[PerformDayUserRecharge](@cardNumber BIGINT, @payValue DECIMAL(18,2), @movementNumber int OUTPUT)
AS
BEGIN
	if (@payValue <= 0)
	BEGIN
		SET @movementNumber = NULL		
		RETURN
	END
	
	DECLARE @message VARCHAR(255)
	DECLARE @MAX_RECHARGE_VALUE DECIMAL(18,2)
	DECLARE @MIN_RECHARGE_VALUE DECIMAL(18,2)
	
	SELECT @MIN_RECHARGE_VALUE = CAST(CAST(value AS VARCHAR(30)) AS DECIMAL(18,2)) FROM Config WHERE [key] = 'MIN_RECHARGE_VALUE';
	SELECT @MAX_RECHARGE_VALUE = CAST(CAST(value AS VARCHAR(30)) AS DECIMAL(18,2)) FROM Config WHERE [key] = 'MAX_RECHARGE_VALUE';
	
	if (@MIN_RECHARGE_VALUE IS NOT NULL AND @payValue < @MIN_RECHARGE_VALUE)
	BEGIN
		SET @message = 'Valor invlido para a recarga.'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		return	
	END
	
	if (@MAX_RECHARGE_VALUE IS NOT NULL AND @payValue > @MAX_RECHARGE_VALUE)
	BEGIN	
		SET @message = 'Valor invlido para a recarga.'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		return
	END	
	declare @accountNumber INT
	declare @sequenceId INT
	
	SELECT 
		@sequenceId = Sequence,
		@accountNumber = AccountNumber
	FROM
		DayUserCards
	WHERE
		code = @cardNumber AND DeactivationDate IS NULL
	
	if (@accountNumber IS NULL)
	BEGIN
			
		SET @message = 'Carto de consumo no ativado.'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		return
	END
	DECLARE @faceValue DECIMAL(18,2)
	
	SELECT 
		@faceValue = FaceValue
	FROM
		CardSequences
	WHERE
		id = @sequenceId
	-- se for valor de face, no haver devoluao
	if (@faceValue IS NOT NULL)
	BEGIN
		IF (@faceValue <> @payValue)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'Valor de recarga no corresponsde ao valor de face do carto.'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			return
		END
		IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM AccountMovements WHERE AccountNumber = @accountNumber) > 0)
		BEGIN
			SET @message = 'No  possvel efetuar recarga em carto de consumo com valor de face.'
			RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
			return
		END
	END
	-- REGISTRA O VALOR PARA O MOVIMENTO DE RECARGA
	DECLARE @movementDate DATE
	SET @movementDate = CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS DATE)
	DECLARE @payMode AS INT
	SELECT @payMode = id FROM Paymodes WHERE PaymentType = 4
	INSERT INTO AccountMovements (AccountNumber, MovementDate, [DateTime], MovementType, origin, value, PayMode) VALUES 
									   (@accountNumber, @movementDate, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 0, 6, @payValue, @payMode)
	SELECT @movementNumber = @@IDENTITY
	
	DECLARE @isRefundable BIT
	SELECT @isRefundable =
	(
		CASE
			WHEN EXISTS(SELECT * FROM Config WHERE [key] = 'MULTICLUBES_CREDIT_REFUNDABLE' AND [value] LIKE 'True') THEN CAST(1 AS BIT)
			ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
		END
	)
		
	IF @isRefundable = 0
	BEGIN
	
		-- ATUALIZA O SALDO DA CONTA SEM DEVOLUO
		UPDATE Accounts SET 
			CurrentBalance = CurrentBalance + @payValue
		WHERE
			AccountNumber = @accountNumber	
	END
	ELSE
	BEGIN
	
		-- ATUALIZA O SALDO DA CONTA COM DEVOLUO
		UPDATE Accounts SET 
			CurrentBalance = CurrentBalance + @payValue,
			RefundableBalance = ISNULL(RefundableBalance, 0) + @payValue
		WHERE
			AccountNumber = @accountNumber		
	END		
END
PerformPayment 
/*
 * Efetua o pagamento do consumo utilizando o cartao de consumo
 * @cardNumber = Nmero do carto de consumo
 * @value = Valor do consumo
 * @password = Senha do carto de consumo (NULL se no houver senha)
 * @description = Descritivo do movimento
 * RETORNA INT = Nmero do movimento gerado no MultiVendas
 * EXCEPTIONS = Dispara exception contendo mensagem tratada para o usurio
 */
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[PerformPayment](@cardNumber NVARCHAR(13), @value DECIMAL(18,2), @hashPassword NVARCHAR(30), @description text)
AS
BEGIN	
	
	DECLARE @message NVARCHAR(255)
	DECLARE @accountNumber int
	DECLARE @movementNumber int
	EXEC @accountNumber = dbo.ValidatePayment @cardNumber, @value, @hashPassword
	IF (@@error > 0) RETURN
	
	if (@accountNumber IS NULL)
	BEGIN	
		SET @message = 'Carto de consumo invlido.'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		RETURN
	END	
	if (@value <= 0)
	BEGIN
		RETURN
	END
	-- REGISTRA O VALOR PARA O MOVIMENTO DE PAGAMENTO
	DECLARE @movementDate DATE
	SET @movementDate = CAST(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS DATE)
	DECLARE @payMode AS bigint
	SELECT @payMode = id FROM Paymodes WHERE PaymentType = 4
	INSERT INTO AccountMovements
	(AccountNumber, MovementDate, [DateTime], MovementType, origin, value, PayMode, comments)
	VALUES (@accountNumber, @movementDate, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 0, 9, -1 * @value, @payMode, @description)
	SELECT @movementNumber = @@IDENTITY
	-- ATUALIZA O SALDO DA CONTA (CurrentBalance e RefundableBalance)
	UPDATE Accounts SET 
		CurrentBalance = CurrentBalance - @value,
		RefundableBalance =
		(
			CASE 
				WHEN RefundableBalance - @value < 0 THEN 0
				WHEN RefundableBalance - @value > CurrentBalance - @value THEN 
				(
					CASE
						WHEN CurrentBalance - @value < 0 THEN 0
						ELSE CurrentBalance - @value
					END
				)
				ELSE RefundableBalance - @value
			END
		)
	WHERE
		AccountNumber = @accountNumber	
	RETURN @movementNumber
END
ValidateCardSequence 
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[ValidateCardSequence](@cardNumber BIGINT, @sequenceId INT OUTPUT, @enabled bit OUTPUT, @sequenceType TINYINT OUTPUT, @creditMode TINYINT OUTPUT, @faceValue DECIMAL(18,2) OUTPUT)
AS
BEGIN	
	SELECT
		@sequenceId = ID,
		@enabled = [Enabled],
		@sequenceType = SequenceType,
		@creditMode = CreditMode,
		@faceValue = FaceValue
	FROM
		CardSequences
	WHERE
		@cardNumber BETWEEN initial AND final
	if (@sequenceId IS NULL)
	BEGIN
		return 0
	END
	ELSE
	BEGIN
		return 1
	END
END
ValidatePayment 
/*
 * Valida o carto, o saldo e a senha.
 * Utilize para verificar se o pagamento poder ser efetuado.
 *
 * @cardNumber = Nmero do carto de consumo
 * @value = Valor do consumo
 * @hashPassword = Senha do carto de consumo j criptografada (NULL se no houver senha)
 * NO RETORNA VALORES
 * EXCEPTIONS = Dispara exception contendo mensagem tratada para o usurio.
 */
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[ValidatePayment](@cardNumber NVARCHAR(13), @value DECIMAL(18,2), @hashPassword NVARCHAR(30))
AS
BEGIN	
	
	DECLARE @message NVARCHAR(128)
	
	DECLARE @accountNumber int
	DECLARE @cardHashPassword NVARCHAR(30)
	DECLARE @maxValueWithoutPassword  DECIMAL(18,2)
	DECLARE @avaliableCredit DECIMAL(18,2)
	DECLARE @isActive BIT
	
	SELECT
		@accountNumber = AccountNumber,
		@cardHashPassword = HashPassword,
		@maxValueWithoutPassword = MaxValueWithoutPassword,
		@avaliableCredit = AvaliableCredit,
		@isActive = IsActive
	 FROM
		McConsumptionCards
	WHERE
		Code = @cardNumber
		
	IF (@accountNumber IS NULL)
	BEGIN
	
		SET @message = 'Carto de consumo invlido.'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		RETURN	
	
	END
	IF (@isActive = 0)
	BEGIN
	
		SET @message = 'Carto de consumo bloqueado.'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 1)
		RETURN	
	
	END
	
	IF (@cardHashPassword IS NOT NULL AND @value > ISNULL(@maxValueWithoutPassword, 0))
	BEGIN
	
		IF (@cardHashPassword <> ISNULL(@hashPassword, ''))
		BEGIN
	
		SET @message = 'Senha incorreta.'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 2)
		RETURN	
	
		END
	END
	
	IF (@value > @avaliableCredit)
	BEGIN
	
		SET @message = 'Saldo insuficiente.'
		RAISERROR (@message, 16, 3)
		RETURN	
	
	END	
	RETURN @accountNumber
END
